Umubare wiyongera wihuta w'ibimenyetso by'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) mu Burayi/Akarere ka Burayi n'Ubwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Ibikorwa by'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19) byerekanye imiterere nk'iyo mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere ka Burayi n'Ubwongereza byemeza ko, nubwo ibyiciro byabyo bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ubunararibonye bw'Ubutaliyani, leta, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigomba kongera imyiteguro yabyo yo guhangana n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazagomba kwitabwaho mu by'ubuvuzi, cyane cyane mu byumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, habonetse abantu benshi barwaye indwara ya Pneumonia, bataramenyekana aho bayivuyemo, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko intandaro y'iyi ndwara ari coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa coronavirus y'indwara ifata imyakura ikaze yo mu mwuka 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko abagera kuri 80% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara z'ubuhumekero zifite cyangwa zidafite pneumonia, abenshi muri bo bakaba barakize.
Mu bantu 14% banduye COVID-19, uburwayi bwa COVID-19 bwiyongera cyane ku buryo bukenera kwitabwaho mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6% barwaye indwara ikomeye cyane ikeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bw'ibanze.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ibitaramo by'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, maze tugereranya n'ibyabaye mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Tugeze aho tugereranya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yageze kure cyane mu karere kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu gikurikirana icyorezo cyo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kinyamakuru cyitwa Eurosurveillance 2020 cyo ku wa 5 Werurwe, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari bo Banyaburayi ba mbere bafite icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'uburwayi bwa WHO.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe n'u Bufaransa ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse baturutse i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 na 15 Werurwe 2020 byombi, habonetse abantu 39,768 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye 1,727 bose, muri bo 17,750 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye 1,441 bose bakaba bari mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubona imibare y'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19
Mu kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bagaragaye mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi, usubirwamo buri munsi saa munani.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, no kuyigereranya n'imiterere yo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'igihereranyo cy'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19, tubaze ibyabaye byuzuye mu minsi 14, bityo dufate ingendo zisanzwe za COVID-19, mu bihugu byose bya EU/EEA na UK, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Turagaragaza kandi imibare y'ubwandu bw'igihugu ku gihugu kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani ugereranyije n'ubw'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama- 15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imikorere y'ibitaramo by'umunsi 14 by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, byakurikiyeho mu Ntara ya Hubei (Thailand) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, buza kwiyongera cyane ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020.
Iyi ngendo yatangijwe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'imibare y'abandura baturuka mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekanye ko hari ukwiyongera kw'ibimenyetso by'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 (Inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ugereranyije n'umubare w'ubwandu mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama- 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ayo makuru yagaragaje ko, kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Area ya Aziya n'Ubwongereza byari byatangaje umubare w'abanduye mu buryo buhuye n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abatangajwe ko banduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Buraya (EEA) no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu mibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo cyongereye ku kigero gihuye mu bihugu byose.
Ibi birimo n'ubwo ibihugu bitandukanye byamaze kugera mu cyiciro cy'uburwayi, uko ubuzima bw'abaturage bwifashe, n'uburyo hashobora kuba hari itandukaniro mu bisobanuro by'uburwayi mu bihugu bitandukanye, n'uburyo bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo COVID-19 yemezwe, harimo no gupima abarwayi nyuma.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twatewe n'iki cyorezo basobanuye ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe byo muri ako karere byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwuzuye.
Kugeza ubu, amakuru y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bitaro no/cyangwa mu bigo nderabuzima by'indembe ku rwego rwa EU/EAA araboneka kuri 6% na 1% by'abanduye gusa (amakuru ntabwo agaragara).
Ariko kandi, amakuru agomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo ashyire hamwe amakuru y'ubugenzuzi arebana n'umubare w'abanduye n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-2011 bugaragaza itandukaniro rinini mu bijyanye n'ubwisanzure bw'ibitanda by'indembe n'ubwisungane mu kwivuza mu Burayi, buturuka kuri 29.2 mu Budage kugeza kuri 4.2 kuri 100.000 mu gihugu cya Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira umutungo munini cyangwa muke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bukomeye n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ku baturage 100.000 mu 2010-2011).
Imiterere y'ibimenyetso bijyanye n'ubwinshi bw'ubwisungane mu kwivuza, hamwe n'ingengo y'imari y'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bitaro ku bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza bifitanye isano n'ibyago >90% birenze ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19, byatanzwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse rya ECDC kuri COVID-19.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi bagaragaye mu turere tw'ibihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bikunze gukorera abaturage bo mu turere runaka, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda by'indembe bikwiye gutangwa ku rwego rw'Icyiciro cya 2 cy'Akarere Gaheruka Gaheruka (NUTS-2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza.
Ku bw'ibyo, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigomba kwitegura uko bizagenda mu gihe hazabaho ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bigo byita ku barwayi, nk'uko byagenze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse rya ECDC riherutse, uburyo bwihuse, bwigenga kandi burambuye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2, mu guhindukira mu buryo bwo kugabanya cyangwa kugabanya, kuko ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'imibare y'abandura, nk'uko byari byitezwe, bushobora kutaha igihe gihagije abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugira ngo basobanukirwe, bemere kandi bahindure ibisubizo biboneye mu gihe bitashyizweho.
Ibipimo byihuse by'ibyago byerekana ingamba zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hariho umwanya muto w'amahirwe aho ibihugu bishobora kongera imbaraga mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku buzima.
Iyo bigenze bityo, urwego rw'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Buraya/EEA rushobora guhura n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na coronavirus y'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3.000 no kwandura abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, cyateje akaga ku bantu.
Kimwe na virusi ihwanye na yo, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kuba yandurwamo n'ibinyugunyugu kandi igateza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Nyamara COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse n'ubwandu buciriritse ugereranyije na SARS, ariko ni indwara yandura cyane kandi yibasira cyane abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, ndetse n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare wiyongera wihuta w'ibitabo bivuga kuri iyi ndwara nshya, iyi ngingo yagerageje gutanga ibisobanuro bihuje n'igihe kandi birambuye ku birebana n'icyo kibazo gikomeje kwiyongera.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze by'indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu, izifata abantu, izifata abantu, izirwara ziterwa n'ubwandu, izirebana n'uko umuntu ashobora kuyirwara, uko yayirwara, uko yayirwara n'uko yayirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikomeje kubazwa, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzatuma dusobanukirwa neza indwara idutera ubwoba kandi tukayirwanya.
Umunsi mukuru wa Spring Festival wo ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru ndetse no mu byumweru bikurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara nshya.
Iyi virusi ihuriye cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS) mu 2003; kubera iyo mpamvu, iyi virusi yahawe izina rya SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara iteza iyi virusi yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gihita gikwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi imaze gutuma haboneka abantu 80.000 banduye COVID-19, aho abasaga 40.000 basubijwe mu byabo, naho abasaga 3.000 barapfuye.
OMS yaburiye ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi w'abaturage" wa mbere kandi ko ishobora kwangiza cyane kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko tubikesha PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yashyizeho urukurikirane rw'ubwandu bwiciwe mu barwayi benshi, hamaze gutangwa ibitabo birenga 200 ku bijyanye na COVID-19, bikubiyemo iby'ubwandu, iby'indwara, iby'imiterere y'umubiri, ibijyanye n'ubwandu, ibijyanye n'ubwandu, ibijyanye n'ubwandu, ibijyanye n'ubwandu n'uburyo bwo kuvura.
Iyi raporo igamije gusobanura neza uko ubushakashatsi mu bintu bishya bigenda byiyongera.
Aho bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na CoV, ari zo Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS, icyorezo cya 2012).
Nanone kandi, turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda indwara no kuzigena, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo byinshi bitarabonerwa ibisubizo, ariko bisaba ko tubisobanukirwa.
Mu buryo buhuje n'umuco, CoVs zibonwa ko ari indwara zitera indwara zitagira icyo zangiza abantu, cyane cyane mu guhitana 15% by'abantu bafite ibicurane 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twabonye virusi za coronavirus ebyiri ziteye indwara cyane ku bantu, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, buri imwe yatumye habaho icyorezo cyatangiye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, hanyuma gikwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi ku kigero cy'indwara n'urupfu.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, COVID-19 ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa ku ishusho ya 1.1, icyorezo cya Pneumonia cy'inkomoko itamenyekana cyatangajwe bwa mbere kivuye i Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'u Bushinwa.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, icyorezo cya CoV cyatangiye.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, habonetse umuntu wa mbere wapfuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, mu ntara no mu bihugu by'abaturanyi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, havuzwe ko hari abantu barwaye indwara y'uburwayi, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko ishobora kwandura mu bantu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, akarere ka Wuhan gashyiriweho guma mu rugo, ndetse n'ingendo zose za rusange zahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bw'ubuvuzi kuri iyi ndwara bwavuze ko, mu barwayi 41 banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bagiranye ikiganiro cya mbere n'isoko ry'ibyokurya by'inyanja rya Wuhan, ryibonekeza nk'ahantu hatangiriye kwandura indwara z'ibikoko bitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyi ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (Igishushanyo cya 2).
Kubera ko ibintu byihuta cyane, umubare ntarengwa n'uburemere bw'icyorezo biracyari gutoranywa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866, bugizwe n'abarwayi 4,021 bemejwe ko bafite COVID-19, bwatanze isura nshya y'icyorezo ikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura abantu bafite imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu kigero cy'imyaka 30-65.
