Glycoprotein y'inkokora cyangwa spike (S) ifata ingirabuzimafatizo zayo, angiotensin exchanger enzyme 2 (ACE 2) na dipeptide peptidase 4 (DPP4) by'umwihariko kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, maze membrane fusion ikabaho.
