Urukurikirane rwa mbere rwa SARS-CoV-2 rwatangajwe ku ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 ni ubwoko bushya bwa beta-CoV bufite imiterere y'ibinyabuzima ihwanye na 99,98% mu bipimo 10 byafashwe; ibipimo byavanywe aho icyorezo cyatangiriye, ni ukuvuga ku isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan muri Wuhan.
Mu buryo bw'ibinyabuzima, SARS-CoV-2 isa cyane na SARS-CoV ugereranyije na MERS-CoV.
Binyuze mu kwinjiza imikorosikopi y'ibinyabutabire, ibice bya SARS-CoV-2 byabonetse mu gice gito cyane cy'uruhu rw'ubuhumekero rw'umuntu.
ACE2 y'umuntu yabonetse ari receptor ya SARS-CoV-2 kimwe na SARS-CoV.
Nyamara, poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifata ACE2 y'umuntu mu buryo bufite imbaraga nke kurusha uko ifata poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bihuje n'uko SARS-CoV-2 ituma habaho ubwandu butari bukomeye nk'ubw'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV mu barwayi.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kandi gushinga poroteyine ngufi nshya ikoreshwa na orf3b na poroteyine ikoreshwa na orf8.
Poroteyine ya orf3b ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uruhare mu gutera indwara za virusi no kubuza IFNβ kuvuga; ariko, orf8 nta mwanya cyangwa imiterere izwi ifite.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou, et al. batangaje ko urusobe rw'umuntu rwuzuye rwa cryo-EM ACE2 ku bumenyi bwa 2,9 Å mu bigo bifite imikorere ya B0AT1 ya asidi ya amino.
Basanze uru ruganda, rufite imiterere ifunguye n'iyikitse, rufite imiterere y'ibinyabutabire n'ingingo zigize ACE2-B0AT1 zishobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, ari na zo zigaragaza ko hari ubwandu bwa CoV.
B0AT1 ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura mu kuvura imiti igabanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Umunyamuryango n'umuhuza
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV bizwi ko byaturutse mu mbogo kandi buri kimwe cyandurira ku bantu binyuze mu mpfizi n'ingamiya.
Mu kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bw'imiterere n'izindi CoV, inyenzi zisabwa kuba ari zo zigize SARS-CoV-2 kuko iyi virusi nshya ari 96% y'ubwoko bumwe na CoV ebyiri zisa na SARS zaturutse mu mbogo zitwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 na bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Icyakora, imiterere y'umwirondoro wafasha virusi kunyura mu ruzitiro rw'ubwoko kugira ngo igere ku bantu ntiramenyekana, kandi inzira y'ubwandu iracyari ku isonga.
Ji, et al. batanze igitekerezo cy'uko inzoka ari zo zitwara virusi kuva ku mukinnyi kugeza ku muntu, ibyo bikaba bikubiyemo kongeramo homologue muri S.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa, bagaragaje ko inguge, inyamaswa y'inkazi y'ibinyamushongo irya ibishyimbo ikunda gukoreshwa mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa, ishobora kuba ari yo ikoresha SARS-CoV-2 ishingiye ku kuba ifite 99% by'imiterere y'imiterere y'imiterere y'imiterere ya CoV iboneka mu nguge na SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko, itandukaniro rya 1% ryakwirakwiriye muri genome yose riracyari itandukaniro rinini; kubwibyo, ibisubizo byemeza nk'ibimenyetso by'urufatiro biracyari kure (Igishushanyo cya 3).
Imiterere y'ibinyabuzima ya SARS-CoV-2 ntiyamenyekanye.
Mu buryo bwa vitro, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho amasaha 48 mu bidukikije byumye no mu gihe cy'iminsi 5 ku 20 °C no ku mwuka wa 40%-50%.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite imiterere nk'iyo.
Byatangajwe ko SARS-CoV-2 itangira kumva urumuri rwa ultraviolet no gushyuha kuri 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; ether, 75% ya ethanol, umuti wica udukoko urimo chlorine, acetic acid, chloroform, n'ibindi bimene by'amavuta, ariko atari chlorhexidine, byangiza virusi.
Muri rusange, abantu bose ntibagira ubwirinzi kuri SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bashobora kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi burambuye bwakozwe ku bisubizo by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, dushobora gusa kwerekeza ku zindi mpuguke za CoV, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo cya 4).4).
Muri rusange, nyuma yo gutera umwirondoro, virusi imenyekana na sisitemu y'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri binyuze mu buryo bwo kumenya uburyo (PRR), burimo C-type lectin-like receptor, Toll-like receptor (TLR), NOD-like receptor (NLR), na RIG-I-like receptor (RLR).
Binyuze mu nzira zitandukanye, virusi ituma habaho imiterere y'ubwandu, ihinduka ry'ingirabuzimafatizo za dendritic, no gukora interferon yo mu bwoko bwa I (IFN) igabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi kandi igateza imbere fagositosis ya antigene ya virusi n'ibinure.
Icyakora, poroteyine N muri SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha virusi kwirinda igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi.
Nyuma y'igihe gito, ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo guhangana n'uburwayi bwagiye bufatanya n'ubw'umuntu kurwanya iyo virusi.
T-insoro, zikubiyemo CD4+ na CD8+, zifite uruhare rw'ingenzi muri ubwo burinzi.
Uturemangingo twa T CD4+ dutera uturemangingo twa B gukora udukoko tw'umubiri tw'ubwoko butandukanye ku virusi, kandi uturemangingo twa T CD8+ twica uturemangingo twanduye virusi mu buryo butaziguye.
Utwo tugingo tugakoraho uturema poroteyine zituma twumva ko turwaye.
Nyamara, CoV ishobora guhagarika imikorere y'ingirabuzimafatizo za T binyuze mu gutuma ingirabuzimafatizo za T zipfa.
Ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, bukubiyemo ibyangombwa, nk'ibya C3a na C5a, ndetse n'umubiri wa antibodies nabyo ni ingenzi mu kurwanya ubwandu bwa virusi.
Urugero, udukoko tw'umubiri twigenga twavuye mu barwayi bakize, twanga MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, imikorere y'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri irenze urugero ituma habaho umubare munini w'ibinyabuzima by'ubwigenge, bishobora gutuma habaho kwangirika kw'ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu mimerere mibi cyane, bigatuma umuntu adakomeza kugira ubushobozi bwo gukora neza bw'imyanya ndangagingo ndetse n'urupfu.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2, igaragazwa n'ibyorezo by'indwara zidakira, yibasira cyane abantu bakuze bafite indwara z'indwara z'indwara zidakira n'abagore batwite.
Muri rusange, abantu bafite virusi mu rugero rwagutse cyangwa bafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara bafite amahirwe menshi yo kwandura kurusha abandi.
Igereranyo cy'igihe cyo kuboneka kwa SARS-CoV-2 ni iminsi 1-14, cyane cyane iminsi 3-7 ishingiye ku bushakashatsi ku bantu 425 ba mbere babonetse mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Icyakora, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 1.099 bwagaragaje ko ingano y'igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro ari iminsi itatu, igera ku minsi 0 kugeza kuri 24.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, bugaragaza ko igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro ari iminsi 4,8 (3,0-7,2) hashingiwe ku mubare w'abantu 8,866 babonetse.
Ni ngombwa ko abayobozi b'ubuzima bagena igihe cyo gukora mu kato neza bashingiye ku gihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro cyihariye, bityo bakarinda abantu banduye ariko batagaragaza ibimenyetso, kwandurira virusi ku bandi.
Nk'uko bisanzwe, abantu bagaragayeho virusi cyangwa bayanduye, ubusanzwe basabwa kuguma mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
