Ubushyuhe akenshi ni ikimenyetso cya mbere cya COVID-19, cyangwa se buherekejwe n'ibindi bimenyetso birimo guhekenya, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo, kuribwa mu maso, kuribwa umutwe, kuribwa mu muhogo, guhohoterwa, kubabara mu gatuza, guhohoterwa, uburwayi bwo mu gatuza no kwitsamura.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagira dyspnea na/cyangwa hypoxemia nyuma y'icyumweru kimwe batangiye kurwara.
Mu gihe indwara ari nyinshi, indwara y'umurwayi ishobora gutera vuba cyane, ikavamo indwara yo guhumeka mu buryo bukabije, indwara yo guhumeka idasanzwe, indwara yo kwiyongera kw'imihindagurikire y'amaraso, indwara yo kwiyongera kw'imikorere y'umubiri, n'indi.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka n'umuriro mwinshi, nubwo nta kibazo cy'imikorere y'ububyimba bw'ibihaha, bagomba gupimwa virusi kugira ngo hamenyekane hakiri kare.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko 98% by'abarwayi bafite umuriro, 76% bafite ububabare, 55% bafite dyspnea, na 3% bafite diarrhea; 8% bakeneye ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi.
Ibyavumbuwe bisa n'ibyo byatangajwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri buherutse gukorwa, ubwo bagenzuraga imiryango n'imiryango byaturukaga ku bantu batagira ingo.
Mu kugereranya, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV bafite umuriro (98%), ububabare bukabije (47%), na dyspnea (55%) nk'ibimenyetso by'ibanze.
Nyamara, 80% by'abarwayi bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka, umubare munini cyane kurusha uw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 kandi uhuza n'ubwandu bwa MERS buruta ubwa COVID-19.
Ibirura (26%) n'umuhogo (21%) nabyo byagaragaraga mu barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, umuriro (99%-100%), guhekenya (29%-75%), dyspnea (40%-42%), diarrhea (20-25%), no kubabara mu muhogo (13-25%) byagaragajwe nk'ibimenyetso by'ibanze kandi inkunga y'umuyaga yasabwaga ku barwayi bagera kuri 14%-20%.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare, impfu za COVID-19 zari 2% ku bantu 66,576 bamaze kumenyekana ku isi hose.
Mu kugereranya, SARS mu Ugushyingo 2002 yahitanye abantu 10% by'abamaze kwandura 8,096.
Ku bijyanye na MERS, hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kwezi kwa Kamena 2012, impfu zageze kuri 37% ku bantu 2,494 bemejwe ko banduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko R0 ya SARS-CoV-2 yageraga kuri 6,47 ku kigero cy'icyizere cya 95% (CI) cya 5,71-7,23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV igera kuri 2 kugeza kuri 4.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV mu bijyanye n'ibimenyetso, urupfu n'ingwara ya R0 byatanzwe mu Mubare 1.
Iyi mibare igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwiza cyane kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko ntiyica nka MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, imbogamizi zo kugenzura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 ziruta cyane icyorezo cya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Akenshi, iyo mibiri iba mu muryango umwe cyangwa mu itsinda rimwe cyangwa mu modoka imwe, urugero nk'ubwato bw'ubwato.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira amateka y'ingendo cyangwa kuba i Wuhan cyangwa ahandi hantu hagize ingaruka cyangwa guhura n'umuntu wanduye cyangwa umurwayi mu byumweru bibiri bya mbere yo gutangira.
Icyakora, hari amakuru avuga ko abantu bashobora gutwara virusi nta bimenyetso byayo bamaze ibyumweru birenga bibiri, kandi ko abarwayi barangije kuva mu bitaro bashobora kongera gutwara virusi, ibyo bikaba byateye abantu kugira amakenga yo kongera igihe cyo kuguma mu kato.
Mu ntangiriro, umurwayi aba afite ingirabuzima fatizo z'umweru (cyane cyane lymphocytes) zisanzwe cyangwa zigabanutse.
Urugero, limfopenia ifite umubare w'amaraso atukura < 4×109/L, urimo umubare w'amaraso atukura < 1×109/L, n'umubare w'indwara ya aspartate aminotransferase hamwe na viremia byazamutse byabonetse mu barwayi 1,099 ba COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'imitobe y'amaraso n'imitsi hamwe na myoglobin byazamutse mu maraso y'abarwayi bamwe, ndetse na poroteyine C-reactive n' umuvuduko w'igihumure mu maraso byazamutse mu barwayi benshi.
Mu barwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye, imibare ya D-dimer, ari byo bihingwa byo gusenya fibrin mu maraso, irazamuka, kandi umubare w'amaraso wagabanuka.
Ubumuga bw'igituza bw'ibishushanyo bugaragara mu barwayi benshi ba COVID-19 kandi bugaragazwa n'igicucu cy'ibihu cyangwa ubumuga bw'ibirahuri mu bihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira indwara z'ibicurane by'ibicurane, gukomereka cyane kw'ibihaha no kugira indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ibicurane (ARDS).
Iyo ARDS ibaye, kubyimba bidategekeka, kwiyongera kw'amazi no kuba umuntu agira imitsi ituma imyuka idakora neza, bituma imyuka idakora neza.
Imikorere mibi y'imyanya y'ubuhumekero yo mu bwoko bwa I n'ubwa II, igabanya igipimo cy'ibinyabutabire by'ubuhumekero kandi igatuma habaho imihangayiko yo kugabanya igipimo cy'imikorere mibi y'imyanya y'ubuhumekero, bityo bigatuma imyanya y'ubuhumekero idashobora kwaguka kandi bigatuma habaho ibyago byo guhomba kw'imyanya y'ubuhumekero.
Ni yo mpamvu, ibisubizo bibi cyane kurusha ibindi ku mafoto y'igituza akenshi biba bihuje n'ibyiciro by'indwara zikomeye cyane.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isuzuma rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryagaragaje ko hari udukoko tw'ibihaha, ko hari udukoko tw'ibihaha, ko hari udukoko tw'ibihaha tw'ibihaha, ko hari udukoko tw'ibihaha twinshi, ko hari n'udukoko tw'ibihaha twinshi mu maraso y'abarwayi bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara, ibyo bikaba bihuje n'isuzuma ry'indwara ziterwa na virusi na ARDS ndetse n'isuzuma ry'indwara ziterwa na SARS na MERS.
Iperereza rya SARS-CoV-2 RNA binyuze mu gukora polymerases z'urufatiro (RT-PCR) ni ryo rigenerwa icyemezo cy'ibanze cyo gusuzuma COVID-19.
Ariko, kubera umubare munini w'ibinyoma by'ibinyoma, bishobora kwihutisha icyorezo, ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gupima (bitagishingiye gusa kuri RT-PCR) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu nk'ibyo ni na ko bimeze ku birebana no kumenya indwara ya SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, guhuza amateka y'indwara, ibimenyetso by'indwara, ibipimo bya laboratwari n'ibya radiyo ni iby'ingenzi cyane kandi ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu ashobore gufata icyemezo cy'uko indwara ari indwara.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye protocol yo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye kuri CRISPR mu kumenya SARS-CoV-2, bwabonye ibice bya SARS-CoV-2 bya RNA ya synthetic kuri 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugeza kuri 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 copies kuri microliter y'inyongera) hakoreshejwe inkoni yo kwibiza mu gihe kitarenze isaha imwe nta bikoresho by'ingorabahizi bikenewe.
Twizeye ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora kongera cyane ubushishozi n'ubworoherane mu gihe bwaba bwaremejwe mu bipimo by'ubuvuzi.
Kubera ko nta bushobozi buhagije bwo kuvura virusi nshya ya COVID-19, abaganga batanga ubufasha mu kwivuza abarwayi ba COVID-19, mu gihe bagerageza imiti itandukanye yari yarakoreshejwe cyangwa yari yarateganyijwe mu kuvura izindi virusi, urugero nka SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (Imbonerahamwe ya 2).
Ubu buvuzi bukubiyemo ubuvuzi buriho ubu n'ubufite ubushobozi bwo gukoreshwa n'imiti ya virusi, imiti yo kurwanya indwara, imiti ya steroïde, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa, n'ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze.
Ndetse n'umushongi w'amaraso wo mu barwayi bakize, washyizweho kugira ngo ukoreshwe mu buvuzi.
Ibigo by'ubuvuzi birimo birwanira hamwe mu gukora udukoko tw'ubwirinzi n'urukingo rwo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Mu cyiciro cya mbere, SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha kandi ishobora no kwibasira izindi ngingo zigaragaza ACE2 ku kigero cyo hasi, nk'imyanya y'ubuhumekero n'impyiko.
Ariko kandi, uburwayi bwo mu mutwe no kubura umwuka ni byo bibangamira cyane abarwayi kandi ni byo bituma bapfa cyane.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi cyane mu guhumuriza ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima, bukubiyemo imiti isanzwe ya ogisijeni, ogisijeni y'umuriro mwinshi, guhumeka mu buryo budateza uburwayi, no guhumeka mu buryo bw'ubumara, bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukomeye bagomba gushyigikirwa na oxygenation ya membrane extracorporeal (ECMO), ni uburyo bwo kwihuta kwa cardiopulmonary buhindurwa bukoreshwa mu kuvura umutima udakora cyangwa guhumeka bibangamiye ubuzima.
Byongeye kandi, kwita ku mibare y'amashanyarazi, kwirinda no kuvura indwara z'ibanze n'isukari, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi na byo ni ingenzi ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
