Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu kwanduza amaso.
Ku bw'ibyo, abaganga na bo bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa cyangwa uturindantoki tw'amaso mu gihe bakorana n'umurwayi.
Ku bantu bose batuye mu turere twanduye cyangwa dushobora kwandura, ni byiza ko buri wese yakwiyuhagira akoresheje isabune isukura indwara kenshi kurusha uko bisanzwe, akagerageza kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo yiyicare wenyine, kandi akirinda guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Abantu bemera ko kuba abantu bareshya n'ibirenge bitatu ari byo bituma umuntu atajya kure y'umurwayi.
Izi ngamba ni uburyo bw'ingirakamaro bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 ari virusi nshya ku bantu, kuba ifite imiterere ihwanye cyane na SARS-CoV, nk'uko byatangajwe ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020, byagombye kuba umuburo ukomeye ku Bushinwa bufite urwibutso rukomeye rw'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003.
Nyamara, ku ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe kugenzura indwara yahumurije abaturage avuga ko iyi virusi nshya ifite ubushobozi buke bwo gukwirakwira no kongera kwiyongera hagati y'abantu, kandi ko kwirinda no gukumira iyi ndwara atari ikibazo.
Ubwo butumwa bwateye ubwoba abaturage cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari mu myiteguro y'umunsi mukuru wa Spring Festival, bityo iki gihe gikomeye cyo kurwanya icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya Wuhan cyari cyaratinze.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara cyo mu Bushinwa cyagombye kuvana isomo kuri ibyo maze kigakora amajyambere akomeye mu gihe kiri imbere.
Urugero, iyo nzego yagombye (1) kuba yitonda mu gihe itanga itangazamakuru rya rubanda kuko ijambo ryose rivugwa n'abaturage riba ribareba kandi rishobora guhindura imyifatire yabo n'imyanzuro yabo; (2) kuba igishishikazwa cyane n'amakuru adasanzwe aturuka mu bitaro aho gutegereza raporo yemewe y'abaganga cyangwa abakozi b'ibanze; (3) kuba igishyiraho imipaka kugira ngo icikishe icyorezo mu bihe byacyo bya mbere, aho kugerageza guhumuriza rubanda; (4) kuba itanga ibiganiro byihariye kandi by'ingirakamaro kugira ngo haboneke ubumenyi bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cy'indwara kandi hagerweho gusuzuma no kunoza uburyo bwo gusubiza abaturage mu buryo buhoraho.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 yatangiye gukwirakwira mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa hose no mu bihugu birenga 50 byo ku isi mu gihe cy'iyi nyandiko.
Kubera ko iyi virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 na SARS bikaba bisa, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangaje ko ari icyorezo cya SARS cyongeye kugaruka.
Icyakora, hari itandukaniro rigaragara hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari na ryo ryangombwa mu kurwanya icyorezo no kwita ku barwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, ibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abagore, kandi igipimo cy'urupfu kiri hejuru mu bantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko.
Imfu za SARS zari nyinshi ugereranyije n'iz'indwara ya COVID-19 (10.91% ugereranyije na 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 batanga virusi nubwo baba badafite ibimenyetso, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bakunze gutangaza virusi mu gihe barwaye cyane. Ibi bituma bigora cyane mu guhagarika ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 ugereranyije na SARS.
Ibi bisobanura impamvu zimwe na zimwe za SARS-CoV-2 zikwirakwira vuba kandi ku buryo bwagutse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ibipimo bya RNA bisanzwe byo gusuzuma SARS-CoV-2 bishobora gutanga ibisubizo bibi ku barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera kugaragaza ko bafite virusi.
Ibyo bintu byagiye bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku buryo virusi ishobora gukwirakwira.
Kubera ko ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 buteye imbere cyane, hari ibibazo by'ingenzi bigomba gukemurwa:
SARS-CoV-2 yaturutse he?
Nubwo twabonye ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite 96% by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bihuza n'izindi virusi ebyiri zisa na SARS z'ikinyugunyugu, ntituramenya neza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku gikinyugunyugu.
Ni izihe nyamaswa zigize umuyoboro wo kwanduza virusi kuva ku muntu ukomoka ku wundi, twavuga nk'ikinyugunyugu?
Ntidushobora guhagarika ku buryo bw'ingirakamaro ubutumwa bwa virusi, kandi icyo cyorezo gishobora kongera gukwirakwira igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo ingero z'imiterere ya molekile n'imiterere ya biochimique byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na ACE2, ni gute virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo igatuma habaho impinduka z'uburwayi?
Ese iyi virusi ishobora no guhuza ingirabuzimafatizo z'izindi ngingo zigaragaza ACE2?
Iyo tutabonye ibisubizo byumvikana by'ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora kubona uburyo bwihuse bwo kubimenya no kubitekerezaho neza, ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubitaho mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza.
Iki cyorezo kizamara igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi ikura mu buryo bw'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo mu gihe ikwirakwira hagati y'abantu?
Ese iyi ndwara izakwira isi yose, irangire nka SARS, cyangwa izagaruke nk'ibicurane?
Ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo hamwe n'ibindi byinshi, ni iby'ingenzi cyane, ariko bishobora gufata igihe kugira ngo tubibone.
Ariko kandi, uko byagenda kose, nta yandi mahitamo dufite uretse guhagarika iki cyorezo vuba uko bishoboka kose kugira ngo dusubire mu buzima busanzwe.
Inkomoko ya koronavirusi y'umuntu
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibihumbi, ihinduka ry'imiterere n'imiterere byatumaga virusi ya corona (CoV) n'iyo ikoreraho, harimo n'abantu, bihinduka.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri ba coronavirus (HCoVs) bari bazwiho gutera indwara zidakomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) n'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS) byahinduye ibintu, byerekana ukuntu ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kwangiza cyane kandi bugatera ubwoba ubuzima.
Igitero cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019 cyatumye CoV yongera kugaragara kandi kidutangaza kubera ko cyandurira cyane, ariko kikaba gifite ubukana buke cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Igituntu cya HCoV ni zoonosis. Bityo, gusobanukirwa inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bizadufasha.
HCoV nyinshi zituruka mu ducurama.
Inzego z'ibanze z'abatuye HCoV zimwe na zimwe nazo zaramenyekanye.
Kumenya inyamaswa zitera indwara bigira ingaruka ku buryo bwihariye ku birebana no kwirinda indwara mu bantu.
Gushakisha imikorere ya CoV-inshuke mu nyamaswa bishobora no gutanga amakuru y'ingenzi ku byerekeye indwara ziterwa na CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi nkuru, dutanga isesengura ry'ibyari bimenyerewe kuri HCoV 7 byibanda ku mateka y'ibyavumbuwe, aho byaturutse mu nyamaswa no mu buryo byanduriraga mu zindi.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko twagereranyije no gutandukanya HCoVs mu buryo bw'ubwihindurize no mu buryo bwo gusubiramo genomes.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya CoV 2019 (COVID-19) kirimo kuvugwa muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, ibisabwa kugira ngo umuntu agire ubushobozi bwo guhinduka n'ingaruka zo guhinduka kwa virusi ku ndwara na byo byashimangiwe.
Virusi ya corona (CoV) ni yo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, igizwe n'itsinda ry'imitsi ya virusi ya RNA ifite uruziga, ifite uruziga rwiza, n'umugozi umwe.
Iyi virusi ifite genome nini cyane iri hagati ya 26 na 32 kilobase mu virusi za RNA yitwa "CoV", kubera imiterere yayo isa n'ikamba munsi ya mikrosikopi ya elegitoroniki.
Ku byerekeye imiterere, CoVs zifite genomes zitari mu bice bifite imiterere isa.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu by'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bigira imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bibiri binini (ORF1a na ORF1b) byisumbuyeho, byombi bihindurwa mu poroteyine z'inyongera pp1a na pp1ab.
Polyprotein ikora indi poroteyine 16 itari mu byiciro by'ibanze, yitwa nsp1~16.
Ibisigazwa bya genome bigizwe n'uruziga rw'ibisobanuro by'ibanze (ORF) ku binyabuzima by'ibanze, birimo utubindi cyangwa utubindi (S), ishusho cyangwa impapuro (E), uruhu (M), na nukleoproteine (N).
Hariho umubare w'ibinyabuzima by'inyongera by'imiterere runaka byandikirwa n'imiterere itandukanye ya CoV.
Hashingiwe ku itandukaniro mu mikoranire y'ingirabuzimafatizo, CoVs zashyizwe mu miryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, na delta-CoV); muri iyo miryango ine, umuryango wa beta-CoV ufite HCoV nyinshi kandi ugabanyijemo imiryango ine (A, B, C, na D).
Ibimenyetso bya phylogenetic byerekana ko udukoko n'udukoko aribyo bitanga ingirabuzima fatizo nyinshi za alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga ingirabuzima fatizo za gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, virusi za CoV zakomeje kunyura mu ruzitiro rw'ubwoko, kandi zimwe muri zo zahindutse indwara zikomeye mu bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana virusi zirimo abantu barindwi (HCoVs).
Muri izo virusi uko ari ndwi, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alpha-CoV.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, virusi ya corona ya syndrome y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS-CoV), virusi ya corona ya syndrome y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV), na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, na HCoV-NL63 ubusanzwe bitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'imbeho na/cyangwa diarrhoea.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, na SARS-CoV-2 ni indwara zandura cyane, zitera ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero mu barwayi benshi cyane kandi zifite amahirwe menshi yo gukomera zikavamo indwara z'ubuhumekero zidakira (ARDS) n'ibimenyetso byo hanze y'ibihaha.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwihariye mu mubiri w'abarwayi ba grippe mu myaka ya za 60.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwakozwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse ku cyorezo cya HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bikaba bitera ibimenyetso byakira.
Mu by'ukuri, hari igitekerezo cyakiriwe cyane cy'uko ubwandu bwa HCoV muri rusange butari bubi, kugeza igihe icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byangije byinshi mu mateka muri iki gihe, aho cyibasiye abantu barenga 8.000 ku gipimo cy'urupfu cya 10%.
Hashize imyaka icumi, icyorezo cy'indwara yo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS) cyatumye habaho icyorezo gikomeje muri Arabiya, kigakwira mu bindi bice by'isi.
HCoV nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV), ikitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni agenga icyorezo cya koronavirusi y'uburwayi 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,120 no kwandura abantu barenga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Amatara yarasakuye kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kigiye kuza.
Izo virusi zose uko ari 7 zaturutse mu mikino yo mu bwoko bwa zoonotic, yaba mu mikino yo mu bwoko bw'ikinyugunyugu, mu bwoko bw'imbeba cyangwa mu bwoko bw'amatungo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bishyigikira ko HCoVs zose zakomotse mu mbogo. Mu mbogo, CoVs zihindura neza kandi ntizitera indwara, ariko zigaragaza itandukaniro rinini ry'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, mu bya siyansi, mu mibereho n'umuco mu Bushinwa no ku isi hose.
Gukurikirana inkomoko ya HCoV mu nyamaswa bitanga uburyo bwo gusobanukirwa amateka y'ibidukikije, imbaraga zituma umuntu ahinduka, n'ibintu bibuza ko habaho kwimuka hagati y'amoko.
Ubu bushakashatsi bushobora no kuyobora cyangwa koroshya ishakishwa ry'ibikoresho by'inyamaswa, ibyangombwa, n'ibikoresho byo kongerera SARS-CoV-2 imbaraga, ibyo bikaba bifite ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi nkuru, dutanga isesengura ry'inkomoko ya zoonotic, ikwirakwira hagati y'amoko, n'imiterere y'icyorezo cya HCoV.
Twagaragaje cyane kandi tuganira ku ngingo rusange y'uko virusi y'ibanze ya HCoV ubusanzwe itari indwara mu byayigize, ariko ikaba indwara nyuma yo kwanduzwa hagati y'amoko mu mikumbi mishya.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ihindagurika rya HCoVs, tubona ko kongera ubushobozi bwo kuyikwirakwiza akenshi bijyana no kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara.
Ibyavuye mu cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 nabyo byaganiriweho muri iyi nkuru.
Imibare y'ibinyabuzima by'imiterere y'ibicurane by'amaraso imaze kumenyekana kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mbere yo kuvanaho bwa mbere HCoV-229E B814 mu mubiri w'abarwayi ba grippe, hari izindi virusi za CoV zari zaravumbuwe mu nyamaswa nyinshi zanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, hamaze kuvumburwa virusi zirindwi za HCoV.
Gusuzuma muri make amateka y'ubushakashatsi bwa HCoV mu buryo bw'igihe (Igishushanyo cya 1) ni icyerekezo cy'ibanze.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwavumbuwe mu cyuma cyo mu nda cy'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bwo mu cyuma cyo mu mutwe mu 1966, nyuma buza gukorerwa mu cyuma cy'amaraso cya WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ibicurane, birimo umutwe, kwitsamura, gucogora, no kuribwa mu muhogo, birimo umuriro n'ubuhumekero bigaragara mu 10~20% by'abanduye.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yavanywe mu mibiri y'ibihimba by'umubiri n'inzira zikurikirana mu bwonko bw'abana b'injangwe.
Igisobanuro cy'indwara ya HCoV-OC43 gisa n'aho gisa n'icy'indwara iterwa na HCoV-229E, idashobora gutandukanywa n'izindi ndwara ziterwa n'ibicurane byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka virusi ya influenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byiganje ku isi hose kandi bikunze gukwirakwizwa cyane mu gihe cy'imbeho mu turere dufite ikirere cyifashe neza.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cyo gukingirwa kwa za virusi zombi kiba kitarenze icyumweru kimwe, gikurikirwa n'igihe cy'uburwayi cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu bitangiye gukora ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E bahise bagira ikibazo cy'ibicurane byoroheje.
Abarwayi bake cyane bafite ubwirinzi bucogoye ni bo bagaragaza ko bafite indwara yo mu muhogo wo hasi.
