Icyorezo cya SARS cya mbere cyavumbuwe mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 8,096 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye bagera kuri 774, bakaba bari mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane itandukanye.
Uretse ubwandu buhambaye, buri cyorezo kigereranywa ko gishobora gutera abantu babiri mu cyiciro cya kabiri, kikaba kigira iminsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7 y'igihe cyo kuboneka, kandi ku munsi wa 10 w'indwara, virusi iba ifite umuvuduko wayo w'ikirenga.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV babanje kugira myalgia, umutwe, umuriro, gucuha no gutengushye, bikurikirwa na dyspnea, guhekenya no guhumeka nabi nk'ibimenyetso by'iterambere.
Lymphopenia, ibipimo by'imikorere y'umwijima bidasanzwe, no kuzamuka kwa kreatin kinase ni ibibazo bikunze kugaragara mu mavuriro ya SARS.
