Beta-CoV y'ingona ihuriye cyane na SARS-CoV-2 yabonetse, igaragaza ko ingona ishobora kugira uruhare mu gutwara cyangwa beta-CoV y'ingona ishobora kugira uruhare mu gusimbuza ibice by'imiterere y'imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo bikiri mu bibazo, nta gihamya igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ari umuntu wayikoze ku bushake cyangwa atabikoze.
CoV yongeye kugaragara cyane kubera icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 giherutse kwaduka.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe n'izindi nyamaswa bwahinduye cyane uko tubona akamaro k'inkomoko y'inyamaswa n'aho HCoV ikwirakwira mu bantu.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, na SARS-CoV-2 byaturutse mu mbogo kandi ko byandurira abantu binyuze mu bantu bakoreshaga imiterere y'ibikoresho.
Kubera ko SARS-CoV yaturutse ku guhura kw'abantu n'inguge mu isoko ry'ibiribwa, birashoboka ko gufunga isoko ry'ibiribwa no kwica inguge zose zari muri ryo ari byo byatanze iherezo ryiza ku cyorezo cya SARS.
Ku bw'impamvu nk'izo, inkoko yagombye kuvanwa ku isoko ry'amazi kugira ngo birinde kwanduzwa kwa zoonotic, bitewe n'uko havumbuwe ubwoko bumwe bwa beta-CoV z'inkoko zifitanye isano rya bugufi na SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, ukuri n'uburyo SARS-CoV-2 yandurira mu bantu binyuze mu nyamaswa z'inkazi n'izindi nyamaswa z'inkazi, bigomba gusobanurwa mu bushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kizaza.
Ku rundi ruhande, MERS-CoV imaze igihe kirekire mu ngamiya zo muri Arabiya.
Izo ngamiya zari ingenzi mu gutwara abantu n'ibintu, kandi zari isoko y'inyama, amata, uruhu n'ubwoya by'abantu bo muri ako gace.
Ingamiya z'Abarabu zakwirakwiriye mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati no muri Afurika.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibishoboka ko twica ingamiya zose kugira ngo dukomeze kurwanya MERS, nk'uko byagenze mu masoko y'inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba mu Bushinwa kugira ngo dukomeze kwirinda ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Mu guhagarika icyorezo cya MERS, hagomba gukorwa uburyo buhamye bwo gukora urukingo rw'ingamiya rukora neza kuri MERS-CoV kandi ruhujwe n'izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu.
Mbere y'uko dukuraho iyi virusi, hari ubundi bwoko bushya bushobora kuvuka bugateza icyorezo.
Hari ubwoko bw'imiti ya zoonotic ikwirakwira mu gasozi.
By'umwihariko, virusi z'ibinyamushongo zishobora kuba zoonotic, ziratandukanye cyane.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo ko izi virusi zo mu nyamaswa zishobora guhinduka no kongera guhura, bigatuma habaho izindi virusi nshya zishobora gukwirakwira mu buryo bworoshye kandi/cyangwa zikaba zarahitana abantu mu gihe kizaza.
Imigenzo yo kurya inyamaswa mu turere tumwe na tumwe two mu Bushinwa yagombaga gucibwa kugira ngo abantu n'inyamaswa badakomeza guhura.
Mu gihe habonetse SARS, MERS na COVID-19, gutegura neza no gushyiraho gahunda yo guhangana na byo birakenewe.
Mu by'ukuri, virusi nyinshi zabayeho ku isi kuva kera cyane.
Izo virusi ziba mu byiciro by'ibanze kugeza igihe zizaba zimaze gukwirakwira.
Nubwo imbeba zifite ibintu byinshi byatuma virusi ikwirakwira, amahirwe y'uko abantu bagirana imibonano n'imbeba n'izindi nyamaswa zo mu gasozi ashobora kugabanuka mu gihe abantu baba baragiye bakirinda inyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Gukurikirana ibinyabuzima bikomoka ku nyamaswa bikeneye gukorwa kugira ngo basobanukirwe neza ikinyabuzima cya CoV n'aho iherereye, bikaba byatuma byorohera mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'imyanya ndangagitsina n'ibyorezo by'indwara.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza cyane bwo kwirinda virusi ya zoonosis ni uko abantu bagomba kwirinda ahantu h'ibidukikije habamo virusi z'ibinyabuzima.
Ibice bimwe by'ikibazo cy'inkomoko ya SARS-CoV-2 ntibiramenyekana.
Icya mbere, niba imbeba zanduza virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa z'ibinyamushongo, ni ngombwa kumenya uko imbeba n'inyamaswa z'ibinyamushongo byatangiye kubana.
Icya kabiri, niba imbeba zifite uruhare rw'ibanze mu kwanduza abantu, uburyo abantu bahura n'imbeba bugomba kugaragazwa.
Icya gatatu, niba hari inyamaswa y'icyamamare ya gatatu ikora nk'umunyamuryango w'inyamaswa y'icyamamare, uburyo ikorana n'izindi nyamaswa, hakubiyemo abantu, ibinyamanswa n'ingona, bugomba gusobanurwa.
Amaherezo, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi z'ibinure, harimo n'amatungo ashobora kuba afite ubukana bwa SARS-CoV-2, haba mu cyorezo cyo kugerageza no mu kugenzura, bigomba gukorwa.
Yaba imbeba, inguge cyangwa ibindi binyabuzima, byitezwe ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi y'umubyeyi wayo isa neza ishobora kuzagaragara mu murwayi wayo w'ibanze mu gihe kizaza.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje muri aka gace buzatuma haboneka inzira y'ihindagurika rya SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa, bigatuma abantu barushaho kwirinda no kugenzura COVID-19.
Ivugurura ry'ibipimo byo gupima abateganya ko COVID-19 yaba yaranduye n'abemejwe ko COVID-19 yaba yaranduye, birakenewe.
