Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19, umubare munini w'abapfa buri munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje abantu bashya batanu bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bishwe n'iyo virusi mu munsi umwe.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo (IEDCR) cyo muri Bangladesh cyatangaje ko abanduye 114 ari bo bakomeje kubaho, naho abakize 33 bakaba bari mu ngo zabo.
Hishwe abantu 17 muri rusange.
Mu itangazo ry'amakuru ryashyizwe kuri internet, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko abapfuye barimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dukurikije uko Dr Meerjady abivuga, babiri bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 60, babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60, n'umwe wari hagati y'imyaka 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu bapfuye bakomoka i Dhaka.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi w'ibitaro yabwiye Anadolu Agency, ikinyamakuru cy'aho, ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komisiyo yo kurwanya ruswa mu gihugu cya Bengali, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Ku wa gatandatu, mu itangazo ry'amashusho ku rubuga rwa interineti, Minisitiri w'Umuhanda n'Ibiraro Obaidul Quader yavuze ko ingendo rusange zizamara igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari byarateganyijwe, kugeza ku wa Gatandatu utaha.
Iyi gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo z'abantu bose yatangiye tariki 26 Werurwe, ikaba iteganyijwe kurangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki 4 Mata.
Itwara ry'ibikoresho by'ibanze - imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa - riracyemewe.
Abantu ba mbere banduye COVID-19 muri Bangladesh, ni abantu babiri bari bavuye mu Butaliyani, ndetse n'umugore w'umwe muri bo, ku itariki ya 8 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, abo bantu uko ari batatu bari barakize.
