Nibura abantu ibihumbi 52 bapfuye bashingiye kuri COVID-19, indwara iterwa na koronavirusi.
Ibi byabereye ku munsi umwe Malawi yemeje ubwandu bwa mbere bwa coronavirus na Zambia ihitana uwa mbere wa coronavirus.
