Ubucuruzi bwo muri Ositaraliya bwimuriyeho imipaka yo kugura umwenda w'isuku
Ku cyumweru no ku wa Gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya ya Woolworth na Coles, yagabanyije imipaka yo kugura umwenda w'isuku, ku buryo ku isoko hose mu gihugu hose hagurwaga amakarito abiri n'akandi kamwe.
ALDI na yo yashyizeho imipaka y'ipaki imwe, ku wa Mbere.
Ibi bihano byatangajwe mu butumwa ku rubuga rwa Facebook.
Abaguzi bavuga ko bakomeje gukusanya ibicuruzwa kubera gutinya COVID-19 mu gihe abaturage bagomba kwigunga.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths kandi yagabanyije kugura umwenda w'isuku wo kohereza mu rugo ku gikapu kimwe ku giciro.
Iryo hinduka rikurikira ihame ryo gufunga amakarito ane ku gicuruzwa, ryagaragajwe na Woolworths na Coles ku itariki ya 4 n'iya 5 Werurwe.
Mu itangazo ryasohowe ku wa 8 Werurwe, Coles yatangaje ko mu gihe hateganyijwe guhagarika ibyo bicuruzwa bine, "ibigo byinshi bikomeje gusohora mu gihe cy'isaha imwe nyuma yo gutangwa", avuga ko ibyo basabye "bitigeze bibaho", mu gihe ALDI, mu butumwa bw'urubuga rwa Facebook ku wa kabiri, yabyise "ibitunguranye".
Ubucuruzi "bwarushijeho kwiyongera" mu cyumweru gishize, nk'uko bivugwa n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths.
Iduka rya Costco ryo muri Canberra na ryo ryagabanyije umubare w'amafunguro ryemereraga abantu kugura ku ma paketi abiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo birinde inzara, Coles yasabye ibicuruzwa byinshi ku babigurisha no kongera inshuro byoherezwa, Woolworths yasabye ibikoresho byinyongera, mugihe ALDI yatumye ibikoresho byo kwamamaza kuwa gatatu byifashishwa mbere.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi bo muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko y'inzego z'ibanze z'ubutegetsi ku bihereranye n'igihe imodoka zitangirwa, bituma bitoroha.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'ibikomoka ku masoko bizamuka, mu gihe ababikora bazaba bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, kandi ko hazabaho ibirori bike.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko kubera ko yafunguriye abantu mbere y'igihe, hari amaduka amwe n'amwe atashoboye gukora ibirori byo ku wa Gatatu.
Mu nkuru ya News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu by'ubucuruzi muri Kaminuza y'Ikoranabuhanga ya Queensland, yavuze ko buri joro amaduka yuzuza ibyokurya.
Yatsindagirije ko umwenda w'ubwiherero ari ikintu kinini ku buryo usanga gifite umubare muto w'ibikoresho, kandi ko iyo ugurishijwe, uba usigaye usigaye usigaye ari ubusa ku buryo usanga ibintu bike cyane.
Coles na Woolworths bavuga ko iyo hari ibintu byinshi ku mbuga, niba ibicuruzwa nk'utuyobyabwenge n'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bishobora kugurwa kandi bikaba byinshi, ubwoba bushobora kugabanuka, Russel Zimmerman avuze kuri ABC News.
Ikigo gishinzwe gukora umwenda w'isuku ukoreshwa mu bikoresho by'ubwogero cyitwa Who Gives a Crap cyavuze kuwa gatatu w'icyumweru gishize ko cyarangiye.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora umwenda w'ubwiherero wa Kleenex, na Solaris Paper, ikora Sorbent, bemeza ko bakora amasaha 24 kuri 24 kugira ngo bakomeze gutanga ibyo bakenera, nk'uko raporo y'ikinyamakuru News.com.au ibigaragaza.
