Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku buryo indwara yageze kure, aho kwerekeza ku buryo ishobora guteza akaga, OMS ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushishikariza leta kugira icyo ikora:
Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyerekezo cy'icyorezo.
Iyo leta ishatse kumenya, gupima, gukemura, gutandukanya no guhuza abaturage bayo, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, yavuze ko ari byo.
Turimo guhangayikishwa cyane n'ubwiyongere buteye ubwoba n'uburemere bwabwo ndetse n'uburyo ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bitinda.
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara, abivuga, iki cyorezo "nta ho gihuriye n'ikindi".
Mu nyandiko CNN yasohotse muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko "nta virusi y'ubuhumekero yigeze ikurikiranwa kuva yatangira kugeza aho ikwirakwira ku isi hose".
Ghebreyesus yavuze ko "nta cyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus twigeze tubona".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi ntitwigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iyi ndwara nshya y'icyorezo yakurikiwe n'icyemezo cyafashwe na OMS mu kwezi kwa mbere cyatangaje ko iyi ndwara ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange gihangayikishije isi yose.
Dr. Anthony Fauci, umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara Zandura n'Abaganga, yavuze ko iby'iki cyorezo "bizaba bibi kurushaho".
