Icyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe nk'Ikibazo cy'Ubuzima rusange ku Isi ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020, cyatangazwa nk'icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri 1.61 miliyoni banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bahitanye abantu bagera ku 97.000.
