Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi umuntu wafashwe ashobora kuba nta bimenyetso agira.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara cyane ni umuriro (88%) n'igisebo (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara harimo umunaniro, gukora imyanda yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (phlegma), kubura ubushobozi bwo guhumeka, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo no mu mitsi, kubabara mu muhogo, umutwe, gutontoma, kwitsamura, haemoptisis, diarrhea, cyangwa cyanosis.
