Ibipimo bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'umwuka cyangwa amaraso.
Ibisubizo ubusanzwe biboneka mu masaha cyangwa mu minsi mike.
Muri rusange, iki kizamini gikorerwa ku musokoro wo mu mazuru, ariko kandi gishobora gukoreshwa no ku musokoro wo mu ijosi.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri ibi bipimo by'ubushakashatsi cyagaragaye ko ari cyo cyakenewe kugira ngo gikoreshwe mu buryo bwagutse.
Muri Amerika, ibipimo bya serolojiya byakozwe na Cellex byemewe gukoreshwa mu bihe by'ubutabazi, gusa bikoreshwa n'ibigo byemewe.
Ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'ibinyabiziga bya radiographie na tomographie (CT) mu bantu bafite ibimenyetso birimo ubukana bw'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri kandi nta byuma by'ibirahuri.
Umuryango w'Abaturage bo mu Butaliyani urimo ushyiraho urubuga mpuzamahanga rw'ibaruramari rw'ibyavumbuwe mu mashusho ku bantu banduye.
Kubera ko hari izindi ndwara zirimo adenovirus, PCR idafite ibimenyetso byemeza ko ari yo yihariye mu kumenya COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bunini bwakorewe mu Bushinwa bwagereranyije ibipimo bya CT by'igituza na PCR, bugaragaza ko nubwo bidakwiriye cyane ku ndwara, kubaga mu buryo bw'imikorere byihuse kandi byoroshye, ari na byo byatumaga abantu bifuza gukoresha ibipimo by'igituza mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Urusobe rw'imikorere y'imikorere y'ubwonko rushingiye ku bwenge bw'ubumenyingiro bw'ibanze rwakozwe kugira ngo rushobore gutahura uburyo bwo gufata amashusho ya virusi hakoreshejwe radiographie na CT.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura iyi ndwara harimo gukomeza kugira isuku mu buryo bwuzuye, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukora ku maso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa mbere yo gukaraba intoki, no gukoresha umwenda mu gihe ukoroye cyangwa witsamura, no kuwutwika.
Abantu bashobora kuba baramaze kwandura bagirwa inama yo kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Ingamba zo kugabanya ubukana nazo zasabwe kugira ngo hatagira ubwandu.
Nyamara, virusi imaze kugera ku rwego rwo gukwirakwira mu baturage mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi imaze gukwirakwira mu baturage, kandi bamwe mu baturage ntibazi aho cyangwa uko banduye. Abashinzwe ubuzima bafasha abantu bashobora kuba banduye bagirwa inama yo kwambara ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda, kwirinda guhura n'abantu, no kurinda amaso.
Gukoresha amakuru y'aho telefoni zigera muri iki gihugu ku bw'izo mpamvu, byateje impungenge z'ibanga, aho Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasabye ko habaho guhagarika ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura.
Porogaramu zitandukanye za mobile zashyizweho cyangwa zashyizweho kugirango zikoreshwe kubushake, kandi kuwa 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi y'inzobere yakoraga ku bisubizo byububiko, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugirango amenye intera yegereye umukozi kuri terefone.
Nyuma y'ibyo, abakoresha bazajya babona ubutumwa iyo bari hafi y'umuntu wavuye mu bitaro by'abarwayi ba COVID-19. Hari ibitekerezo bitari byo ku buryo bwo kwirinda kwandura; urugero, gukaraba amazuru no gukaraba mu maso n'umuti wo guhanagura umunwa ntibikora.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 rubaho, nubwo hari imiryango myinshi irimo gukora kugira ngo irushyiremo.
Gukaraba intoki ni byiza mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
CDC isaba ko abantu bakaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje isabune n'amazi mu gihe cy'amasegonda nibura makumyabiri, cyane cyane iyo bamaze kuva ku cyumba cy'ibonaniro cyangwa iyo intoki zabo zisa n'izanduye; mbere yo kurya; na nyuma yo gukata, gukorora cyangwa gukorora.
Ibyo biterwa n'uko, hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi yicwa n'isabune yo mu nzu yangiza urusobe rw'ubwirinzi bwayo.
Byongeye kandi, CDC isaba gukoresha umuti wo gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu kunywa inzoga ufite nibura inzoga 60% ku kigero iyo nta sabuni n'amazi biboneka.
OMS isaba abantu kwirinda gukora ku maso yabo, amazuru cyangwa umunwa mbere yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubuso bushobora kwanduzwa hakoreshejwe umuti (mu munota umwe w'ibisasu byanduza ku buso bw'icyuma kitagira ingese), harimo etanol 6271%, isopropanol 50100%, sodium hypochlorite 0.1%, peroxide ya hidrogene 0.5%, na povidone-iodine 0.27.5%.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuboneza urubyaro, urugero nka benzalkonium chloride na chlorhexidine gluconate, ntibukora neza.
CDC iratangaza ko mu gihe hari abantu bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko banduye COVID mu bigo rusange, urugero nk'ibiro cyangwa aho abana barererwa, ahantu hose hakoreshwa ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki, urugero nk'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rwa elegitoroniki, ibyuma by'ikoranabuhanga, ibyuma by'ibikoresho, ibyuma by'ibikoresho, na za ATM zikoreshwa n'abantu barwaye, bigomba gukoreshwa imiti yo kugabanya ubukana bw'ubwandu.
Amashami y'umuryango wita ku buzima avuga ko abantu bagomba guhisha umunwa n'amazuru yabo bakoresheje umufuka cyangwa umufuka mu gihe barwaye cyangwa barwaye, kandi ko bagomba kuwutesha ako kanya.
Amasasu yo kubaga ni ingirakamaro ku bantu bashobora kuba baranduye kubera ko kwambara masike bishobora kugabanya ingano n'uburebure bw'amazi atemba mu gihe umuntu avuze, atemye no mu gihe atemye.
OMS yashyizeho amabwiriza ku gihe n'uburyo bwo kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, umuhanga mu by'indwara z'ubwandu muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yagize ati "kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya abantu bakunze gukora ku maso yabo bakoresheje intoki zitanduye, ari na zo soko y'icyorezo".
OMS isaba abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, nk'abantu bita ku barwaye COVID-19, nubwo OMS yemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda ko bakora ku maso yabo.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byatangiye gushishikariza abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC isaba gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'umubiri twakozwe mu myenda. Ubushinwa bwihariye bushishikariza gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi dukoreshwa rimwe mu baturage bafite ubuzima bwiza, cyane cyane iyo begeranye (1 metero (3 ibirenge) cyangwa munsi) n'abandi.
Hong Kong yashyizeho amabwiriza yo kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe umuntu arimo atwara abantu cyangwa mu gihe ari mu ruhame.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima muri Tayilande bashishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'imyenda mu rugo no kuzajya tudahanagura buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Czech na Slovakia bibuza abaturage kujya mu ruhame batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa batwikiriye amazuru n'umunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abaturage bayo bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame kugira ngo bibarinde n'abandi.
Guverinoma ya Otirishiya isaba umuntu wese winjira mu kigo cy'ubutabazi kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bayo bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu ruhame.
Tayiwani, ikora udupfukamunwa miriyoni 10 ku munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye abagenzi bo mu mihanda ya gari ya moshi n'amabisi yo mu mijyi gutwara abantu mu buryo bw'umubiri kwambara udupfukamunwa guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata.
Panama isaba abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa igihe cyose bari hanze, kandi isaba abantu badafite ubushobozi bwo kugura udupfukamunwa kwikorera.
Ibipfamatwi nabyo bikoreshwa cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Gukumira abantu (byitwa no kubarinda ku mubiri) ni ingamba zo kurwanya indwara zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya cyane cyane abantu bagirana imishyikirano ya bugufi.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya imikorere y'abantu mu buryo bw'umubiri, harimo kubabuza kujya mu ngo zabo; kugabanya ingendo; no gufunga amashuri, aho bakorera, ibibuga by'imikino, amazu y'imikino cyangwa amazu y'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gushyiraho uburyo bwo kugabanya imibonano mpuzabitsina, bakaguma mu rugo, bagabanya ingendo, bakirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, bagakoresha amagambo yo gusuhuzanya atagira aho ahurira n'abandi, kandi bakirinda gutandukanya abantu.
Muri iki gihe, leta nyinshi zashyizeho cyangwa zashishikariza abantu kwirinda mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare munini w'abantu bateranira hamwe wateganyijwe n'inzego za leta z'Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima wahise ugabanuka, uva ku bantu 250 (niba nta cyorezo cya COVID-19 kizwi mu karere) ugera kuri 50 nyuma y'aho ugera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije guteranira ahantu hahurira abantu benshi. Abageze mu za bukuru n'abantu bafite uburwayi bw'ibanze nka diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso, n'uburwayi bwo mu buryo bw'umubiri bufite ibyago byo kurwara indwara zikomeye n'impamvu z'indwara zikomeye, CDC yasabye ko mu gihe bishoboka baba mu ngo zabo mu duce dufite icyorezo ku rwego rw'abaturage.
Gukoresha ijambo "kugabanya imibonano mpuzabitsina" byumvikanisha ko abantu bagomba kwigunga mu buryo bwuzuye kandi ntibakangurire abantu gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi binyuze mu bundi buryo.
Muri izo nama harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu mubana gusa kandi udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Kwigunga mu rugo ni ingirakamaro ku bantu basanganywe COVID-19 n'abantu bakekwaho kwandura.
Inzego z'ubuzima zatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwisanzura mu buryo bukwiriye.
Amabwiriza yo kwicungira ukwabo akomeye cyane yashyizweho ku bantu bari mu byiciro by'abari mu kaga.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragaragayeho ubwandu bwa COVID-19 n'abantu baherutse kujya mu bihugu cyangwa uturere dufite ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 bagirwa inama yo kwishyirira mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bashobora kuba baraherukaga guhura na COVID-19.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura icyorezo ni ukucyumira cyangwa kucyirinda, ndetse no kucyicisha.
Gukumira bikorwa mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gutandukanya abantu banduye no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu no gukingira bigamije guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu baturage bose.
Iyo bitagishoboka gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara, imbaraga zikurikiraho zijya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya: izi ngamba zifatwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira no kugabanya ingaruka ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Imikorere y'ubushakashatsi n'ubushakashatsi byakozwe mu rwego rwo kubara imikorere y'ibinyabutabire.
Gukuramo birasaba ingamba z'ubutagondwa mu guhindura icyorezo kugabanya umubare w'ubwandu ku kigero kiri munsi ya 1. Igice cyo gucunga icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni ugushaka kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo, bizwi nko kugabanya icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo gutinda ku buzima no gutanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Gutanga imiti mu kurwanya icyorezo birimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwicungira ukwabo; ingamba ku rwego rw'abaturage zigamije gukumira imikorere y'umubiri, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro rusange; guhuza abaturage mu rwego rwo gushishikariza kwakira no kwitabira bene izo ngamba; hamwe n'ingamba ku rwego rw'ibidukikije, nko gusukura ubutaka. Ibindi bikorwa bikomeye bigamije kugabanya icyorezo byakozwe mu Bushinwa mu gihe icyorezo cyari kigenda kirushaho kwiyongera, nko gushyiraho ihagarikwa ry'umujyi wose no gushyiraho gahunda z'urugendo zikomeye.
Ibindi bihugu na byo byashyizeho ingamba zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho uburyo bwo kugenzura abantu benshi no kubacumbikira mu gace kamwe, ndetse itanga n'umuburo ku bijyanye n'aho abantu banduye bajya.
Singapore itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye bakora isuku ku giti cyabo kandi igatanga ibihano bikomeye ku batayikora.
Taiwan yazamutse umusaruro w'ibikoresho byo mu maso kandi itegeka ko habaho kwiyongera kw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo kugabanya ubukana bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abashaka kuvurwa ku kigero cya bibiri bya gatatu, n'urupfu ku kigero cya kabiri, ariko bigatuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa, kandi bigatuma imibereho y'abarwayi irushaho kuzamba.
Gukumira birashoboka, ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikiri mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze kuboneka, niba ari rwo rwa mbere rukiboneka), kuko bitabaye ibyo, ubwandu buzasubira inyuma vuba cyane igihe ingamba zo kumira zizoroha.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo bigira ingaruka ku mibereho y'abaturage n'ubukungu.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi wa COVID-19 wemewe, ariko ibikorwa byo kuwukora birimo gukorwa, harimo no kugerageza imiti isanzwe.
Kunywa imiti ya frigo igurishwa ku buntu, kunywa amazi ahagije no kuruhuka bishobora kugufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso byaho.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'iyo ndwara, umuntu ashobora gukenera umwuka wa ogisijeni, umuti wo mu maraso, n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Gukoresha imiti ya siporo bishobora gutuma umurwayi arushaho kuremba.
Bimwe mu bintu byari byemewe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi birimo gusesengurwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS ivuga kandi ko "uburyo bwo kuvura bwa gakondo n'ubw'iwacu" bushobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
OMS yavuze ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza serivisi z'ubuzima ku bikenewe n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ari intambwe y'ibanze mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere bya OMS mu Burayi byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo bihindure uburyo mu byiciro bitandukanye, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gukora ibizamini bya laboratwari byo gupima COVID-19, igihe bishoboka guhagarika uburyo bwo kwihitiramo, gutandukanya no gutandukanya abarwayi ba COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'abahumeka umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku nkomoko y'icyorezo cya mbere (cyitwa "umurwayi wa zeru").
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanyeho coronavirus nshya yabonetse ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wariyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi bibazo ahanini bifitanye isano n'isoko rya Huanan ry'ibiribwa by'inyanja, na ryo rigurisha inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo kivuga ko virusi ikomoka mu bwoko bumwe bw'inyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, virusi ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan babwiye bagenzi babo ko bari bafite "virusi ya SARS".
Bane muri abo baganga, harimo na Li Wenliang, bahawe umuburo n'abapolisi kubera ko bakwirakwije ibihuha, naho undi witwa Ai Fen, acyahwa n'umuyobozi we kubera umuburo yatanze.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan nyuma yaho yashyize ahagaragara itangazo ku mugaragaro ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, imenyesha OMS.
Umubare munini w'abanduye icyorezo cya Pneumonia bataramenyekana wahawe amakuru n'inzego z'ubuzima za Wuhan, nyuma y'aho zatangije iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati muri Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'u Bushinwa, iterwa n'impunzi zagiye zihunga mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'icyunamo kandi kubera ko Wuhan ari ikigo cy'ingendo n'urugendo rw'ama gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje abantu bashya bagera kuri 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri mu mujyi wa Beijing n'umwe mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Amakuru y'ibanze yakurikiyeho yerekana ko abantu 6,174 bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku wa 20 Mutarama 2020.Ku wa 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zarenze u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani ku mubare w'abamaze kwandura kurusha abandi ku isi.Ku wa 9 Mata 2020, abasaga miliyoni 1.61 bamaze kumenyekana ku isi; abarenga 97,000 bapfuye abandi barenga 364,000 barakira.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 n'uturere bifite nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije Uburayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho amabwiriza yo kugenzura imipaka.
Igisubizo cy'igihugu cyose gikubiyemo ingamba zo gukumira, nka Guma mu rugo (zwi nka Guma mu rugo, itegeko ryo guhunga mu rugo, cyangwa Guma mu Karere) n'amasaha y'ijoro. Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu bwoko bw'amabwiriza yo gukumira mu Karere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu Karere muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu Karere muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miliyari 1.3 bari mu Karere mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari mu mimerere yo kugenzura akarere, bikuraho abantu miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko arwaye COVID-19 ashobora kugaragara ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itaremezwa igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye ari ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Muganga Zhang Jixian yabonye itsinda ry'abarwayi ba pneumonia bataramenyekana icyateye ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza; ibyo bitaro byabimenyesheje CDC ya Jianghan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere by'imiterere y'umuntu ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byagaragaje ko hari virusi ya SARS.
Itangazo ry'umuturage ryashyizwe ahagaragara na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
WHO yabimenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Igihe iyo nama yatangiraga, abapolisi bari baragabishije abaganga bo muri Wuhan ko "bakwirakwiza ibihuha" by'icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'u Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya igaragara" y'ikwirakwira ry'umuntu ku wundi.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye nyuma y'aho bushyizwe ahagaragara n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping nk'"intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Muri Guma mu rugo yavuzwe ko ari "iy'ingenzi mu mateka y'abantu", cordon sanitaire yatangajwe ku ya 23 Mutarama guhagarika ingendo zijya no kuva i Wuhan, kandi yagutse mu mijyi 15 yose yo muri Hubei, igera kuri miliyoni 57 z'abantu.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite birabujijwe mu mujyi.
Umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya wa Lunar (itariki ya 25 Mutarama) wahagaritswe mu bihugu byinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, Huoshenshan Hospital, byarangira mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hakurikiyeho ikindi bitaro, ari cyo Leishenshan Hospital, kugira ngo gifashe abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan, nk'ikigo cy'amakoraniro n'ikibuga, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho ingamba z'inyongera zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku ba mukerarugendo no kongera iminsi mikuru y'umunsi w'impeshyi.
Amashuri yose n'amashuri yose yo mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macau kagiye gashyiraho ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane mu byerekeye amashuri na za kaminuza.
Ingamba zo gukora mu buryo bwa kure zashyizwe mu bikorwa mu bice bimwe by'Ubushinwa.
Imihango yo kugabanya ingendo yashyizweho mu gihugu no hanze ya Hubei.
Imihanda ya rusange yavuguruwe, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo mu Bushinwa yose yafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, nyuma y'uko icyorezo cyinjiye mu cyiciro cy'isi, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda "kwinjiza" virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 y'igenzura ry'abashyitsi mpuzamahanga bose binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, icyorezo kimwe rukumbi cy'Abashinwa cyagaragariye mu gihugu iminsi itanu mbere yaho, muri iki gihe cyaturutse ku muntu wari uvuye i Istanbul mu mujyi wa Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwandurira mu gihugu mu by'ukuri ryabaye ingirakamaro kandi ko icyorezo cyabaye mu butegetsi mu Bushinwa.
Ingendo z'abantu ku munsi umwe zaruhutse muri Hubei, uretse Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo kwirinda. Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga ya Repubulika ya Rubanda yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizasubikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru arambuye yerekeye igihe iyi politiki izarangirira.
Abantu bashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 30 Werurwe, leta y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura no gutanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bigo by'ubucuruzi. Inama y'igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kwibuka by'agateganyo itangira iminota itatu yo guceceka ku rwego rw'igihugu ku ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri, mu gihe cya Festival ya Qingming, nubwo leta y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango guha icyubahiro ku buryo bwa interineti mu kwita ku mabwiriza yo kwirinda icyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 20 Gashyantare, inzego z'ubuzima z'igihugu zatangaje ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura wiyongereye cyane, ahanini bitewe n'ikoraniro ry'ishyaka rishya ry'idini rya Daegu, rizwi nka Shincheonji Jesus Church.
Abayoboke ba Shincheonji bari basuye Daegu baturutse i Wuhan, ni bo bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye habaho icyo cyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iryo dini, 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13% bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abasaga 2.000 ni bo bari bamaze kumenyekana muri Koreya, ku ya 29 Gashyantare bakaba bari bageze ku 3.150.
Inzego zose za gisirikare za Koreya y'Epfo zimaze gufungirwa mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu ba Koreya y'Epfo bapimwe bagasanga banduye virusi.
Ibihe by'indege nabyo byagize ingaruka kandi birahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ifatwa nk'iy'ingenzi kandi yateguwe neza ku isi yo gupima virusi mu baturage, gutandukanya abantu bose banduye, no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura harimo gushyiraho itegeko ryo gutanga amakuru ku giti cyabo ku bantu bavuye mu mahanga bakoresheje porogaramu za telefoni, gupima virusi mu buryo bw'ibanze cyangwa ku buryo bw'imodoka ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu barenga 20.000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yafashwe nk'iyigamije kugabanya icyorezo nubwo nta mujyi wose wahawe ubwigenge.
Abanyakoreya benshi basinye inyandiko isaba ko Perezida Moon yafungwa kubera ko bavuga ko leta yakoze amakosa mu guhangana n'icyorezo, cyangwa se bagashimagiza uko Perezida Moon yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umubare muto w'abanduye umunsi umwe mu byumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bageraga mu gihugu bavuye mu bindi bihugu bari kujya mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo imaze kwakira ubutumire bw'ibihugu 121 byo gufasha mu gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje ku wa 19 Gashyantare ko ifite icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kandi, nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu by'Ubuvuzi ibivuga, abantu babiri bapfuye uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'indi mihango y'umuco, imikino, n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, ndetse no gufunga kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyize muri gahunda miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twibasiwe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imigi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imigi rwari rugeze mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi rwarakomeje.
Ahantu ho gusengera mu bayisilamu mu mujyi wa Qom hagumye hagaragara kugeza ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Hagati y'ibivugwa ko icyorezo cya Iran cyahishiriwe, ibihugu birenga icumi byahise bishyira abarwayi muri Irani ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, bigaragaza ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 leta ya Irani yari yatangaje kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho 23 mu bagize 290 bashyizwe mu kato ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura byimazeyo abarwanashyaka ba Human Rights Defenders bafunzwe kubera imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite ibyangombwa.
Bavuga ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira mu bigo by'imbohe, nk'ibigo by'imfungwa, nabyo bidafite ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari bo benshi mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 cyangwa abayobozi ba leta ya Irani bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ihanganye n'ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus bugera kuri 50 buri saha n'urupfu rushya buri minota icumi.
Dukurikije uko umutegetsi umwe wa OMS yabivuze, birashoboka ko muri Irani hari abantu bakubye incuro eshanu abo byagiye bivugwa ko banduye.
Byongeye kandi, byavuzwe ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'imari mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Burenganzira bwa Muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroherezwa ibihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bapimaga ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abanduye bakomeje kwiyongera cyane bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zijya n'izava mu Bushinwa ndetse itangaza ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu.
Nyuma yaho, habonetse amatsinda y'abantu badafite aho bahuriye na COVID-19, batangira ku bantu 16 bemejwe muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo kugabanya icyorezo, rivuga ko abantu barenga 50.000 bo mu mijyi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani bagomba kuguma mu kato.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "mu turere dufite icyorezo, abantu ntibemererwa kujya hanze.
Gufungura imirimo n'imikino byategetswe muri ako karere. "Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu cyose mu gihe Ubutaliyani bwari bwujuje umubare w'abapfuye 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A, izaba yabereye mu nzu z'amacumbi kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose izaba yahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi, usibye amaduka manini n'amafashini. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri Rikuru ry'Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi, Gusubiza Ubuzima n'Ubuvuzi bw'Ibibazo Bikomeye (SIAARTI) ryasohoye inama z'imyitwarire y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye na protokoli ya triase ishobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa mu bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abapfuye ba coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga raporo y'abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'igisirikare zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ku ya 5 Mata, hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kumenyekana ko banduye, 15,887 bapfuye, naho 21,815 bakize mu Butaliyani, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yavuze ko ibintu byateje umubare munini w'abapfa ari uko mu Butaliyani hari abantu benshi bageze mu za bukuru, kandi ko nta bushobozi bwo gupima abantu bose banduye virusi buhari.
Mu mizo ya mbere, u Bwongereza bwagize icyo bukora ku cyorezo ari kimwe mu bihugu byagize icyo bigezaho, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'u Bwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho ingamba zo kugabanya imibereho y'abaturage cyangwa gushyira abantu mu kato.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe kubera ko yafashwe nk'igisubiza nabi kandi idafite imbaraga mu gusubiza impungenge z'abaturage. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje asaba ko habaho guhagarika ingendo zose n'imikoranire idakenewe kandi agasaba abantu gukora mu rugo, niba bishoboka, no kwirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, mu masoko no mu bitaramo.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro, nka za pub n'amazu yimyitozo ngororamubiri, bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya kwishyura abakozi bagera kuri 80% by'umushahara kugeza ku gipimo cya £2,500 ku kwezi kugirango birinde ubushomeri muri iki gihe cy'ihungabana. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira imibonano y'abantu barenga babiri no kugabanya ingendo no gukora hanze gusa kubikorwa bifatwa nk'ibikenewe cyane.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'ingamba zabanje, iyi mipaka yashyizweho n'abapolisi binyuze mu gutanga ibihano no gusesa imbaga.
Ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi byategetswe gufunga, uretse ibyo bitaga "by'ingenzi", bikubiyemo amaduka manini, amaduka y'imiti, amabanki, amaduka agurisha ibikoresho by'ibyuma, za sitasiyo z'ibikoresho by'amashanyarazi n'amazu y'ubwubatsi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, habonetse umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko arwaye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa leta ya Washington, mu mugabo wari watashye avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Ku ya 29 Mutarama, itsinda ry'abakozi ba White House ba Coronavirus ryashyizweho.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubuzima bw'abaturage kandi bushyiraho ingamba zo guhagarika kwinjira ku bantu baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara, ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya leta ya Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyateguye uburyo bwacyo bwo gupima.
Nyamara, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatinze gutangiza igerageza ku buryo zatumye umubare w'icyorezo w'ukuri utagaragara icyo gihe.
Ibizamini byahungabanyijwe n'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi by'ibura ry'ibikoresho byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta ku bikoresho by'ubushakashatsi bitemewe na leta (n'abanyeshuri, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, n'ibipimo by'ihagarikwa ry'abantu bakwiriye kwipimisha kugeza mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe (amategeko y'abaganga akaba ari ngombwa nyuma yaho).
Kugeza ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyatangaje ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika hakozwe ibizamini bitarenga 4.000.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hateganyijwe ibipimo bike cyane bitageze ku 14.000.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yagize iti "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso n'amabwiriza y'abaganga bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo bapimwe". Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika rwavuzwe muri leta ya Washington ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu, icyo gihe ibindi bihugu na byo bifata umwanzuro.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zabwiwe ingaruka z'icyorezo gishya cya coronavirus ku gihugu cy'iki gihugu n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo muri Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko riha inkunga y'ibikoresho by'ubutabazi by'ubwikorezi bwa Coronavirus, riha agera kuri miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari y'ubutabazi bw'ibanze ku bigo bya leta mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe ategeka abakozi kutagira ingendo, akabuza inama, kandi agatera abakozi inkunga yo gukorera mu rugo.
Ibirori n'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko yahagaritse ingendo ku bice byinshi by'u Burayi, usibye Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, byatangira ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yaguye uwo mupaka awugeza mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu cyose gifite ikibazo cy'ubukungu, bityo amafaranga ya leta akaba ari yo akenewe mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibikorwa byinshi by'ubucuruzi byafunze cyangwa bigabanyije amasaha y'akazi muri Amerika yose mu rwego rwo kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu bihugu byose 50 no mu Ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, New York City yatangaje ko ifite 10,700 z'abanduye coronavirus, zirenze umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri wa New York yavuze ko ingamba zo kwirinda abantu benshi zisa n'izigenda zikora neza kuko imibare y'abandura yariyongereye cyane, kuva ku minsi 2.0 kugeza ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32,308 bemejwe ko banduye muri New York City, ndetse 672 bapfuye bazize iyi virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zifite abanduye coronavirus benshi kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kugabanya imikorere y'abaturage kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bwitwaga USNS Comfort, bwari ubwato bw'ibitaro bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwashyize ku cyambu i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yari ifite umubare munini w'abantu 884 bapfuye bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Muri leta ya New York, abanduye barengaga 100.000 ku ya 3 Mata. White House yanenzwe kubera ko yagabanyije iterabwoba no gucunga ubutumwa binyuze mu gutegeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza itangazo rusange n'ibitabo bijyanye na virusi mu biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Muri rusange, abantu bose bemera uburyo Trump yakemuye ikibazo cy'ibibazo by'ubukungu, bagabanijwe mu matsinda y'abafite aho bahuriye n'ibibazo by'ubukungu.
Abategetsi b'Amerika bamwe na bamwe n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika ku byo gukenera ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi biva mu Bushinwa, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi.
Isesengura ry'ingendo zo mu kirere ryakoreshejwe mu gupima no guhanura uburyo bwo gukwirakwiza kandi ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'amakuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 yatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'ingendo zo mu kirere, abantu benshi baturuka i Wuhan bari i Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari byo bihugu bikunzwe cyane n'abantu baturuka i Wuhan.
Bali yagaragaye ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi buke mu bijyanye no kwitegura mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yagaragaye ko ifite ubushobozi buke.
