Kubera ubwigenge bw'ingendo rusange bwashyizweho muri Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu bimwe na bimwe biteganya guhungisha abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba diplomasi mu karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ndege z'abakozi ba leta z'iwabo, byemerewe n'ubuyobozi bw'u Bushinwa.
Kanada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, u Buyapani, u Buhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, Argentine, u Budage na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byatangiye gahunda yo guhungisha abaturage babyo.
