Interaktion yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Philippines ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, umuryango wa Croix Rouge wa Singapore watangaje ko ugiye kohereza imfashanyo z'amadolari y'Amerika miliyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje impano ya miliyoni 18 z'intoki z'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda 10,000 ya Hazmat, na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ndetse zitanga n'inguzanyo y'amadolari y'amamiliyoni 100 y'amafaranga yo gufasha ibihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho by'ibizamini miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyenda 60,000 yo kurinda umubiri i Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, kugira ngo bitangirwe Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho, yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100.000, n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka mu buryo bw'umwuka muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze imfashanyo z'imiti muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech byatangaje impungenge ku ireme ry'amasike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye ibikoresho 58,000 by'iperereza bya coronavirus byakozwe n'Abashinwa bifite amanota 30% gusa; mu gihe Ubuholandi bwo bwakuye 600,000 by'amashuha y'amaso y'Abashinwa afite inenge.
U Bubiligi nabwo bwasubije inyuma udupfukamunwa 100.000 tutakibasha gukoreshwa, twitwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, imfashanyo z'u Bushinwa zakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku wa 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije igikorwa cy'ubutabazi bw'ubutabazi bw'ibihe bidasanzwe ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye ingufu leta y'Ubushinwa yagize mu gucunga no gukumira icyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004 aho abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga guhishira ibintu bituma bigora ibikorwa byo kwirinda no gukumira, n'ikibazo cyo muri iki gihe aho leta y'u Bushinwa "itanga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo irinde ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu kwitabira icyemezo cya guverinoma y'ibanze cyo gushyiraho gahunda yo gutwara abantu n'ibintu i Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo iyo ngingo "ntago ari inama ya OMS", ariko ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyo kwiyemeza gukumira icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane" ndetse avuga ko "kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu bahuriye mu bantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'imibare y'abandura mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cy'uburwayi bw'abantu ku isi (PHEIC), icyiciro cya gatandatu cya PHEIC kuva cyatangira gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC yasobanuwe kubera ko hari "akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bikennye n'ibifite amikoro ari mu rwego rwo hagati, bitagira gahunda nziza y'ubuzima.
Mu gusubiza ku bijyanye no gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zo kubangamira ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi bitari ngombwa" kandi ko "WHO idashishikariza abantu guhagarika ingendo n'ubucuruzi".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ibikorwa by'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikennye, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushyigikira ibihugu "bifite uburyo bwo kugenzura abantu banduye virusi mu gihe habaye icyorezo".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "imbaraga zacu ziri ku ntege nke cyane" asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura amafaranga menshi nyuma". Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku wa 11 Gashyantare, OMS yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara y'iyi virusi.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye António Guterres yemeye gutanga "igisubizo cyo gutanga imbaraga zose z'umuryango w'Abibumbye".
Nyuma y'aho, Umuryango w'Abibumbye washyizeho itsinda ry'abafite inshingano zo gucunga ibibazo kugira ngo bashobore guhuza ibisubizo byose by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, ibyo bikaba byaratumye OMS ivuga ko "bishobora kwibanda ku bikorwa by'ubuvuzi, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gukoresha ubuhanga bwazo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo mu rwego rw'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi ba China bahuje ibikorwa riyobowe na OMS ryatangiye; rigamije guha abadepite mpuzamahanga na OMS mu Bushinwa mu rwego rwo gufasha mu buyobozi bw'imbere mu gihugu no gupima "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'indwara" binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'igihugu bireba no gukora ingendo zo ku butaka kugira ngo harebwe "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo kurwanya mu ntara no mu ntara, zirimo mu mijyi no mu byaro". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus" kandi ivuga ko, nubwo hakiri kare cyane kuvuga icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba kuguma mu "gihe cyo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cyateye muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abakozi ba ONU ry'ubumwe muri Irani kugira ngo basuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko igipimo cy'ibyago bya coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi kizazamurwa kiva ku "cyinshi" kijye ku "cyinshi cyane", iki kikaba ari cyo kigero cyo guhaguruka cyane kandi ari cyo kigero cyo hejuru cy'ibyago.
Mu itangazo, Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima, yatanze umuburo ugira uti "iki ni cyo gihe kugira ngo ubutegetsi bwose bwo ku isi bujye buhura n'ukuri: Nimuhumure.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuza iwawe kandi ugomba kwitegura", kandi asaba ko ingamba zo kuyikumira zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemerera abayobozi b'ubuzima rusange gutangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza icyorezo bisobanura ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azahura n'icyo cyorezo".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO yavuze ko WHO "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere n'uburemere by'icyorezo, ndetse n'uburebure bw'ibikorwa by'ubwirakabiri". WHO yakiriye ibitutsi bikomeye kubera ko yafatiwe mu buryo budakwiriye mu guhangana n'icyorezo, harimo no gutinda gutangaza ko hari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange no gushyiraho icyorezo.
Kimwe mu bitero by'urujijo byatewe n'uko abantu 733.000 bashyize umukono ku ibaruwa yo ku wa 6 Mata, yoherereje Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, asaba ko yegura.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu za ONU zibarirwa mu bihumbi zashimangiye kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu wese mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Iryo tsinda ry'abahanga ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gukora ibikorwa by'ubutabazi, kandi ko leta ari yo igomba kubikora.
Iryo tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bidakwiye gukoreshwa nk'impamvu yo gutandukanya abantu b'amoko runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, hakubiyemo abafite ubumuga, abantu bo mu madini mato, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi, abatagira aho baba, abakennye cyane, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bantu bakeneye inkunga za leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe imiyoborere irimo gukora ibishoboka byose ngo ihangane n'ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage ziterwa na COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi ku Burezi n'Igihugu by'Amajyaruguru ryashyizeho gahunda yo gutanga amakuru ajyanye n'igihe kandi yuzuye ku bisubizo by'amabwiriza mu bihugu byo ku isi hose, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gukomeza sisitemu y'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'amavuriro y'akarere n'imihango yo gutembera, ikigo cya digitale kirimo abacungagereza politiki y'igihugu, kandi kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi no korohereza igisubizo cy'isi yose gihuje mu guhangana n'imbogamizi za coronavirus.
Ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa bwashyigikiwe n'Abanyamerika, Minisitiri w'Ibiro by'Abaminisitiri by'u Bwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, ku bijyanye n'uburyo bwafashe icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abakozi b'intara b'ishyaka ry'aba-communiste ry'u Bushinwa (CPC) birukanywe mu rwego rwo gucunga ibikorwa byo gukumira icyorezo mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, bikaba ari ikimenyetso cy'uko batishimiye uburyo inzego za politiki zafashe mu guhangana n'icyorezo mu karere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bemeza ko iyi ngingo igamije kurinda Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira ibitekerezo by'abahuza umugambi wa COVID-19 ko cyaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubutegetsi bwa Amerika bwa Donald Trump bwise coronavirus "virusi y'Abashinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan" buvuga ko "ibikorwa by'Ubushinwa byo kwihishahisha ari byo bituma virusi ihinduka icyorezo cyugarije isi".
The Daily Beast yabonye ubutumwa bwa leta ya Amerika busobanura uburyo bwo gutangaza amakuru kandi bugaragara ko bwaturutse mu nama y'umutekano w'igihugu, buvuga ko "byose byerekeye u Bushinwa.
Tubwiwe kugerageza no gutanga ubu butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo ikiganiro n'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo". Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy, na Bloomberg byemeza ko ingufu z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo ari kimwe mu byo itangazamakuru rigamije kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "ingingo ya politiki ya politiki, ikubiyemo intambara yo kugira ingaruka binyuriye mu guhindura ibintu mu buryo butari bwo no 'kugira neza mu buryo bw'ubukungu.' "
Borrell yongeyeho ko "Ubushinwa bwiyemeje gushishikariza abantu kumva ko, mu buryo butandukanye n'uko Amerika yabibona, ari cyo gihugu cyabo cy'ubufatanye kandi cyiringirwa".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ndetse buvuga ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'amasaga 100.000 yo guha Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bashinjwa kandi ko bakwirakwiza imfashanyo zari zigenewe ibindi bihugu, bakazishyira mu bihugu byabo.
Hari kandi n'amakimbirane ajyanye n'ibikoresho byo mu maso yavuzwe mu bindi bihugu, urugero nk'u Budage, Otirishiya n'u Busuwisi; kimwe na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho bihumuriza bibarirwa mu magana byari bigenewe igihugu cya Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko EU itagaragariza ubufatanye Ubutaliyani bwahuye n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwitabiriye ku buryo bwa bilateral.
Birumvikana ko ibyo bidatanga igihamya cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'u Burayi".
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo guhabwa telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yohereje ingabo z'u Burusiya kohereza abasirikare b'abaganga, imodoka zihariye zo guhanagura indwara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo yavuzwe n'"abantu bakomeye mu bya politiki" bavuga ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'u Burusiya "zitagira icyo zimarira u Butaliyani cyangwa se ko nta cyo zikumariye".
Uwo muyobozi yavuze ko Uburusiya bwakoze ibitero by'ubushyamirane "bwibisanzwe n'ubutegetsi bw'isi n'ubw'ikirenga".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani Luigi Di Maio, birengagije ibyo bitangazamakuru maze batanga amagambo yo gushimira.
U Burusiya kandi bwohereje indege itwara imfashanyo z'ubuvuzi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Dmitry Peskov, umuvugizi wa Kremlin, yavuze ko "igihe [Putin] yatangaga ubufasha ku bavandimwe be bo muri Amerika, yatekerezaga ko niba abacuruzi b'ibikoresho n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bo muri Amerika babona uburyo, na bo bashoboraga gusubiza mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defender 2020" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye n'ibihugu bya Baltique, ni yo myitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO ikomeye cyane kuva intambara y'ubutita irangira, izaba ku kigero gito.
Umunyamabanga mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, iyi myitozo ntabwo iteza akaga ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi biyifatanyamo gusa, ahubwo kandi iteza akaga abaturage b'ibihugu bakoreramo". Guverinoma ya Irani yibasiwe cyane n'iki cyorezo, aho abagera kuri babiri bacye b'abadepite banduye hamwe n'abanyapolitiki cumi na batanu bariho cyangwa ba mbere.
Ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa isaba ubufasha avuga ko igihugu cye kigorwa no kurwanya icyorezo kubera kubura uburyo bwo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyateye Amerika gusaba ko yakira politiki z'imibereho myiza zisanzwe mu bindi bihugu bikize, zirimo ubwisungane mu kwivuza, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihemba, n'amafaranga menshi yo gushyigikira ubuzima rusange.
Impuguke mu bya politiki ziratekereza ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku mahirwe ya Donald Trump yo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida ya 2020.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'ubwirinzi bw'abatuye mu Buyapani" nyuma y'aho u Buyapani butangarije ko umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twashyizweho na leta.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abantu bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari bafite ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku birebana n'uko Perezida Moon Jae-in yari yitabiriye icyo kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi basinye inyandiko zisaba ko Moon yafungwa, bashingiye ku byo bavuga ko leta yakoze nabi mu guhangana n'icyorezo, ndetse banashima uko yabyitwayemo.
Hari bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko ibyo bishobora gutuma leta ikomeza kwibanda ku butegetsi.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yayo yatoye kwemerera Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, gutegeka mu buryo budafite igihe ntarengwa, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko n'amatora rusange, no guhana abantu bafatwa nk'abavuga ibinyoma kuri virusi n'uburyo leta ikemura ibibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatewe n'ibibazo by'ibura ry'ibikoresho, byaturutse ku kwiyongera kw'ibikoresho ku isi byose byo kurwanya icyorezo, kugura ibintu mu buryo bwo guhungabana, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikorwaremezo.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze umuburo ku kibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abaguzi bakomeje kubyifuza ndetse n'ababikora bakabura ababibashakira.
Hari n'ahandi abantu baguye mu rujijo bagura ibintu by'ibanze, urugero nk'ibyokurya, amasahani n'amazi yo mu mazi yafashe mu mazi, bituma habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'amazi.
By'umwihariko, inganda zikora ikoranabuhanga zaratanze umuburo ku birebana no gutinda gutanga ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije uko umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, abifuza ibikoresho byo kwirinda indwara babyifuza, biyongereyeho incuro 100.
Ibyo byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro 20 z'ibisanzwe, kandi bituma habaho guhagarika gutanga imiti mu gihe cy'amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Ibi kandi byateje ubukene bw'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku isi hose, kandi OMS iratangaza ko ibyo bishobora gushyira ubuzima bw'abantu mu kaga.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatanze amahirwe mashya ku bagura daigou yo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye amata y'inshumbusho aba make muri supermarket zimwe na zimwe, amaherezo aza guhagarikwa na guverinoma ya Australia.
Ingamba z'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko bw'ibikoresho by'ibanze zagize icyo zigeraho ku buryo inzara zikomeye zari zitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru zashoboraga kwirindwa.
U Butaliyani bw'Amajyaruguru, bufite umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi, ntibwagize igabanuka rikomeye, ariko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka nk'uko bivugwa n'abahagarariye inganda.
Amazu y'ibyokurya adafite ibyokurya yabonetse by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa barimo barekura inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo barebe ko abaturage bafite ibyokurya bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani na ho hari itegeko nk'iryo risaba abahinzi kubika ibyokurya mu gihe habaye ibintu nk'ibyo.
Iterambere ry'ubukungu ku isi ryamaze kugaragara mu Bushinwa: nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku ya 16 Werurwe, ubukungu mu Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba leta yafashe zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwagabanutseho 20,5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari ikigo cy'ubukungu n'inganda nini, icyorezo cya virusi giteganyijwe ko kizabangamira cyane ubukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu cya Economist Intelligence Unit yavuze ko isoko rizakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe hazaba hagiye haboneka igitekerezo cyumvikana cy'ingaruka zishobora kuza.
Muri Mutarama 2020, abahanga bamwe na bamwe bagaragaje ko ingaruka z'ubukungu bw'iki cyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Impuguke zo muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis zemeza ko icyorezo cyateje ingaruka zisaga miriyari 300 z'amadolari ku muyoboro w'ibikoresho ku isi, zishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Ishyirahamwe ry'Ibihugu Bitanga Ibiribwa (OPEC) ryavuze ko "hari impagarara" nyuma y'uko ibiciro bya peteroli byagabanutse cyane bitewe n'uko ibyifuzo by'u Bushinwa byagabanutse.
Ku ya 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imari ku isi yose yaramanutse kubera ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge zikomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo bitandukanye by'imigabane ya Amerika, birimo NASDAQ-100, S&P 500, na Dow Jones Industrial Average, byanditse kugabanuka gukomeye cyane kuva mu 2008, aho Dow yagabanutseho amanota 1,191, ku munsi umwe gusa ari bwo bwagabanutse cyane kuva mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'imari ryo mu 2007-2008
Ibipimo by'imigabane bitatu byasoje icyumweru biri hasi cyane ku kigero cy'ipesenti 10.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje igipimo cy'inguzanyo ya leta y'Ubushinwa, ariko igumana Outlook Ntagatifu.
Imigwi yongeye kugwa kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ku munsi wa 16 Werurwe habaho kugabanuka gukomeye.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
