Ibizamini bya laboratwari by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 bikubiyemo uburyo bwo kumenya ko virusi iriho n'uburyo bwo kumenya ko hari udukoko tw'umubiri twakoze mu gusubiza ubwandu.
Kuhaba kwa virusi mu bipimo byemejwe na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki kizamini ni icy'umwihariko kandi kigamije kureba SARS-CoV-2 gusa.
Ibi bipimo bikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu bushya cyangwa bukiriho.
Gucukumbura ingirabuzimafatizo (serology) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibipimo by'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu bamaze kwandura, harimo abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo bitagomba gutangwa cyangwa batagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Imibare y'indwara y'indwara y'indwara n'ubwirinzi bw'abantu mu baturage bishobora kwemezwa n'ibisubizo by'ibi bipimo.
Kubera ko ibipimo ari bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bijyanye n'umubare w'abandura virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyakoze ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu mubare w'ibizamini ibihugu byakoze.
Ibyo bishobora no kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, ishobora kuba iri hejuru cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kwanduza imikorere y'ubwoko bwa polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), ubu bushakashatsi bushobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe hakoreshejwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo gusukura mu mazuru cyangwa gupima mu maso.
Ubusanzwe, ibisubizo biboneka mu masaha make cyangwa se mu minsi ibiri.
Iperereza rya RT-PCR ryakorewe ku muntu wafashwe n'indwara yo mu muhogo, ryagaragaye ko ari ryiza mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma y'igihe, virusi ishobora guhita ikurwa mu muhogo mu gihe ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ubundi, ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ibikoresho by'ibipimo bishobora gukurwa mu nzira y'ubuhumekero bw'imbere hakoreshejwe catheter yo mu muhogo cyangwa ibikoresho bikururwa binyuze mu guhumeka (sputum) bishobora gukoreshwa.
Kimwe mu bipimo bya PCR bya mbere cyatangijwe i Charité, Berlin, muri Mutarama 2020 gikoresha imikorere ya polymerases mu gihe cy'ukuri (rRT-PCR), kandi cyashyizeho ibikoresho by'ipima nibura 250,000 byo gukwirakwiza na OMS.
