Gukaraba intoki, nanone byitwa isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki umuntu akora agamije gukuraho imyanda, amavuta, udukoko duto duto cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu buryo buhoraho mu "gihe cy'akaga" runaka k'umunsi, bibuza indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ibicurane na kolera, kwandura mu buryo bw'amaraso.
Nanone kandi, umuntu ashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane, iyo atareze intoki ze mbere yo gukora ku maso ye, ku zuru rye cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga mu mwuka).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu gihe cy'umunsi cyo gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni: mbere na nyuma yo gusama, nyuma yo gusukura umwana cyangwa kumuhindura agapfukamunwa, mbere yo kumucira, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gutunganya inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko zitagifuwe.
Iyo amazi n'isabune bidahari, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umukungugu.
Mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku barwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura indimu cyangwa gukaraba umwana umaze gukoresha ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo gukaraba, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku byokurya byayo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Isuku y'amaboko yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bifitanye isano n'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kuvurwa bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki ni ukuzikuraho udukoko dutera indwara (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho by'ubumara bishobora guteza akaga cyangwa indwara.
Ibyo ni iby'ingenzi cyane cyane ku bantu bakorana n'ibiribwa cyangwa mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko ni na ko bimeze ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara zandura; gukumira ibitera gucibwamwo; kugabanya ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa mu gihe cyo kubyara mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko kongera imikorere yo gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma umwana muto arushaho gukura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazira indwara z'ubuhumekero n'ibicurane ushobora kugabanuka binyuriye mu gushyiraho ibintu byoroheje byo mu rwego rw'imyitwarire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Icyo gikorwa cyoroshye gishobora kugabanya umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara hafi 50%.
Gahunda z'ubutabazi zituma abantu bakaraba intoki zishobora kugabanya indwara z'ibicurane ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu; izi ngamba zishobora gukorwa binyuze mu gutanga amazi meza mu duce dufite amikoro make.
48% yo kugabanya ibyago byo gucibwamwo bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bumwe rukumbi bukora kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda gucibwamwo n'ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero bukomeye (ISPA), nk'imyitwarire idashyize mu gaciro ikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage hirya no hino ku isi.
Pneumonia, ari yo ISPA y'ibanze, ni yo mpamvu ya mbere ituma abana bapfa bakiri bato; ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'ibihaha n'imyimba bihitana abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni eshatu n'igice buri mwaka.
Dukurikije uko UNICEF ibivuga, kugira akamenyero gakomeye ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya ku bwiherero bishobora gukiza abantu benshi kurusha inkingo cyangwa ubundi buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kuvura, kandi bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abapfa bazize gucibwamwo, n'icya kane cy'abapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye.
Gukaraba intoki ubusanzwe bijyanirana n'indi myitozo ngororamubiri mu rwego rw'amabwiriza y'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki nanone birinda impetigo yandurira mu bantu bakorana imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ingaruka nke zo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutera kwangirika kw'uruhu biturutse ku kumera kw'uruhu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 muri Danimarike bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira uruhu rufite inkovu n'ibisebe, byitwa eczema y'intoki cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, cyane cyane mu bakozi b'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane na byo byagiye bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara yo guhangayika bikabije (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ingenzi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu gutaka: mbere na nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (kugeza amazi mu cyumba cy'uburiro, guteka), nyuma yo gusukura umwana (kuhindura agapfukamunwa), mbere yo kumucira, mbere yo kurya na mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gutunganya inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko zitagifite intungamubiri.
Indi mimerere y'ingenzi yo gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye kugira ngo wirinde kwandura indwara, ni mbere na nyuma yo kuvura ibikomere; nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora cyangwa guhumeka; nyuma yo gukora ku byondo by'amatungo cyangwa ku bindi bikoresho by'amatungo; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune uracyari hasi.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwerekanye ko ku kigero cya 38.7% by'ingo zikoresha isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ari yo ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cya 97%, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ziri hagati na 77%, n'Ubushinwa ku kigero cyo hasi cya 23%.
Gahunda y'Ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ishyirwa mu bikorwa na Minisiteri y'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'ingamba zikwiye zo gushyigikira ubuzima n'uburezi by'abana.
Gutanga umuti wo gukiza ibiheri kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune no gusukura amenyo buri munsi n'ibikoresho bya fluoride, ni byo by'ingenzi muri iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
Iyo gahunda kandi yashyizwe mu bikorwa muri Indoneziya.
Gukaraba udukoko duto cyane mu ruhu byongerwaho n'amazi cyangwa isabune.
Akazi k'ibanze k'isabune n'umutoza ni ukugabanya inzitizi z'umuti no kongera ubushobozi bwo kuwusenya.
Amazi yonyine ntashobora gusukura neza uruhu kubera ko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bigize imyanda iboneka mu mubiri, bidashobora kuboneka mu mazi.
Nyamara kandi, gutunganya ibinure n'uduce turimo proteyine bifashwa no kugenzura amazi ahagije.
Isabuni ikomeye, kubera ko ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, ishobora kuba irimo mikorobe yavanywe mu bikoresho by'ibanze.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwakorewe ku birebana n'uko bakayiriya ishobora kwimuka mu mazi y'isabune, bwagaragaje ko nta bushobozi bwo kuyimura ifite kuko iyo sabune iba yarasheshe.
Nyamara kandi, CDC ivuga ko "ibinyobwa by'isabune bitemba bitakoreshwa n'intoki ari byo bikunzwe".
Isabuni yo kurwanya umusemburo yashishikarizwaga cyane abantu bari bazi neza iby'ubuzima.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yica udukoko cyangwa imiti yo kugabanya ubukana bw'imiti ari byiza ku binyabuzima birwanya imiti.
Icyakora, amasabune arwanya mikorobe arimo imiti isanzwe irwanya mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, ifite urutonde rw'imitwe y'ibinyabuzima birwanya mikorobe.
Bityo rero, nubwo ubwoko bw'imiti idashobora kurwanya mikorobe butashoboraga kwifashishwa mu gukingira abantu, ishobora kuba itari ifite imbaraga nk'izo abantu bakoresha mu gucuruza.
Usibye surfactants n'ibikingira uruhu, uburyo buhanitse bushobora kuba burimo aside (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactate acid) nk'umuyobozi wa pH, aside ya benzoate nk'intangabuzima zikora, n'ibindi bihumuriza uruhu (ibinyamushongo by'ingona, vitamini, ibinure, umusaruro w'ibimera). Isesengura ryimbitse ryakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon mu Ishuri ry'Ubuzima bw'abaturage ryerekana ko isabune isanzwe ari nziza nko gusukura antibacterial ya ba nyirabyo irimo triclosan mu gukumira indwara no gukuraho udukoko ku ntoki.
Amazi ashyushye yo gukaraba intoki, ntaba ashyushye bihagije kugira ngo yice za mikorobe.
Utwo ducurama dukura vuba cyane iyo turi ku kigero cy'ubushyuhe bw'umubiri (37 °C).
Amazi ashyushye afite isabune arusha amazi akonje afite isabune imbaraga zo gukuraho amavuta kamere, kuko atuma habaho imyanda n'udukoko.
Icyakora, mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babyizera, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta cyo byamumarira mu kugabanya mikorobe ziri mu biganza.
Gucukura intoki cyangwa gutwika intoki ni uburyo bwo gusukura butariho amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 90 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bitagira amazi, byitwa ibijumba by'amaboko by'inzoga (byitwa kandi ibijumba by'amaboko by'inzoga, ibijumba by'amaboko by'ubumara, cyangwa ibijumba by'amaboko by'ubumara) byatangiye kumenyekana.
Byinshi muri ibi bikoresho byo gusukura bikoreshwa mu buryo bworoshye, bivanze na isopropylique ya alcool cyangwa ethanol, bivanze n'ikintu cyubaka nk'umushongi wa Carbomer (polymeri ya acrylic acid) mu buryo bwa gels cyangwa se bivanze na humektane nka glycerine mu buryo bw'umunyonge cyangwa mu buryo bwa foam, kugira ngo byorohere gukoresha kandi bigabanya ingaruka zo gukama za alcool.
Kongera peroxide ya idorojeni mu kinyange byongera ibikorwa bya antimicrobial.
Gucika inzoga bica za bagiteri, za mikorobe zidakira imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), za bagiteri ziterwa n'indwara y'igituntu, za virusi zitandukanye (harimo virusi ya VIH, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, grippe na hepatite), na za mikorobe.
Kunywa inzoga 70% byicisha 99,97% (kugabanya log 3.5, bisa n'igabanya 35 decibels) ya bagiteri mu ntoki nyuma y'amasegonda 30 nyuma yo kuyinywa na 99,99% kugeza 99,999% (kugabanya log 4 kugeza 5) ya bagiteri mu ntoki nyuma y'iminota 1 nyuma yo kuyinywa.
Inzoga zikorerwa mu gukaraba intoki ntizikora neza ku ndwara ya norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ikaba ari yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Imbere n'inyuma y'amaboko yombi, ku mpande no ku mpera z'intoki zose, bifata amasegonda 30 kugeza igihe amazi, uduhu cyangwa umutobe bikamye.
Ibigo by'Amerika bishinzwe kurwanya no kurwanya indwara (CDC) byashishikarije abantu gukaraba intoki aho gukaraba intoki, cyane cyane iyo intoki zabo zisa n'izanduye.
Gukoresha cyane ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bitewe n'uko byoroshye kubikoresha kandi bikora vuba ku byorezo; ariko, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki ntibigomba gukoreshwa mu buryo bwo gusukura intoki neza, keretse gusa iyo habonetse isabune n'amazi.
Gukoresha imiti yo gukiza intoki ikoreshwa mu kunywa inzoga kenshi bishobora gutuma uruhu rugira ubukana, keretse iyo habonetse imolien n'ibindi bihumanya uruhu.
Ingaruka zo gukama za alcohol zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa gukurwaho binyuze mu kongeramo glycerin na/cyangwa indi emollients muri formule.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, isuku y'amaboko ishingiye kuri alcohol irimo emolien ituma uruhu rutera uburibwe n'umwikubo muke ugereranyije n'isabune n'ibinyobwa byo kwiyeza.
Indwara y'uruhu itera indwara z'uruhu, indwara y'uruhu rw'uruhu cyangwa se kurwara indwara yo kwiheba cyangwa se kurwara indwara yo kwiheba.
Kuba nta ngaruka mbi ziterwa no guhura n'indwara z'uruhu bitera, ni byo bituma iyi miti iba nziza cyane kurusha gukaraba intoki n'amazi n'isabune.
Nubwo ari ingirakamaro, imiti itarimo amazi ntiyakuraho ibintu by'ibanze mu ntoki, ahubwo ikayisiga gusa.
Niyo mpamvu, konji ituma intoki zidakora neza nk'amazi n'isabune mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi kuko zishobora kuba zikiri ku ntoki.
Uburyo ibiyobyabwenge bita alcohol bikora neza cyane biterwa n'ibikoresho bikoreshwa n'uburyo bikoreshwa, kandi mu mateka, ibi bikoresho by'ubuhumekero bikora nabi cyane kurusha inzoga n'ibinyobwa bisukura intoki.
Vuba aha, uburyo bwakoreshejwe bukoresha benzalkonium chloride bwagaragaye ko bugira ibikorwa by'ubumara bikomeza kwiyongera nyuma yo kubinywa, mu buryo butandukanye n'inzoga, aho imbaraga zabwo zagaragaye ko zigabanuka nyuma yo kubinywa kenshi, wenda bitewe n'ingaruka z'ingaruka z'ubwoko runaka.
Abantu benshi bo mu midugudu ikennye ntibashobora kugura isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ubutaka.
Ivu cyangwa umukungugu bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi, ariko ntibigire ingaruka nziza nk'iz'isabune.
Hari impungenge ko iyo ubutaka cyangwa umukungugu byandujwe na mikorobe bishobora gutuma indwara zikwirakwira aho kugabanya.
Kimwe n'isabune, umwotsi ni umuti wica imibu, kubera ko iyo uhuye n'amazi, uba ari umuti ufite ingufu.
OMS isaba ko umukungugu n'umusenyi byajya mu mwanya w'isabune mu gihe nta yo iboneka.
Gukaraba intoki neza, nk'uko bitangazwa n'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara, mu kwirinda kwandura indwara, bikubiyemo izi ntambwe zikurikira:
Jya ukaraba intoki ukoresheje amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Amazi atemba ni yo ateganywa kuko imisarani ihumeka ishobora kuba ifite ubwandu, mu gihe ubushyuhe bw'amazi nta cyo bwagize.
Jya ukaraba intoki zawe ukoresheje isabune nyinshi, ushyire no ku mugongo w'intoki, ku ntoki no munsi y'iminwa.
Isabuni ikuraho udukoko twanduza indwara, kandi ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abantu bakunda gukaraba intoki neza cyane mu gihe bakoresha isabune kurusha igihe bakoresha amazi gusa.
