Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni ikoreshwa ry'uburyo bwo kwirinda no gukumira icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugabanya ibyago mu kazi biterwa n'aho ukorera n'inshingano ufite, bishingiye ku gupima ibyago byo kwandura, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'impamvu z'ibyago ku bakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago byo kudahura n'ubwandu buke gafite aho gaherera ku kazi n'abandi bakozi; kuri aka kazi, hatangwa inama yo kwirinda indwara z'ibanze, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu bitaro mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka, no gukora isuku no guhumeka ahantu h'akazi buri gihe.
Akazi gafite ibyago byo kwandura kagereranywa n'akazi gasaba ko umuntu agirana imishyikirano ya bugufi cyangwa kenshi n'umuntu utazwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19, ariko ashobora kuba yaranduye kubera ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu baturage cyangwa se urugendo mpuzamahanga.
Iri tsinda rikubiyemo abakozi bafite aho bahurira n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu h'akazi hari abaturage benshi, n'amazu acuruza ibicuruzwa byinshi.
Gucunga ibyago kuri aba bantu, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe ibyuma bihumanya umwuka bikora neza, kwirinda gusinzira no gutanga ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi mu gihe umuntu ahuye n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu mirambo bagaragarijwe abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19 nk'abafite ibyago byo kwandura cyane, bikura bikagera ku ndwara yo kwandura cyane iyo umukozi akoze igikorwa cyo gukora aerosol ku muntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba arwaye COVID-19, cyangwa agafata cyangwa agakora ku bipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba arwaye COVID-19.
Gucunga ibyago bikwiye ku bakozi bikubiyemo gucunga uburyo bwo gukora, urugero nk'aho umuntu aba afite umwuka mubi, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikwiye mu kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutinjira ku kazi bitewe n'uburwayi, kuba bagomba kwita ku bandi, cyangwa se bitewe no gutinya ko bashobora kuhagera.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, haba mu bihereranye n'ibikoresho bisabwa cyangwa uburyo bwo kubikenera (nk'uko guhaha nyuma y'amasaha y'ikiruhuko, binyuze mu kohereza cyangwa mu buryo bw'umubiri).
