Iyo COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwo kugenzura neza ni ubuhanga, hakurikiraho kugenzura mu rwego rw'ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakagirwa n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
