Ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu mahame cyangwa imikorere y'akazi, bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (APD) byafashwe nk'ibidashobora gukoreshwa cyane kurusha ibyuma by'ikoranabuhanga n'ibiro by'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukumira igice cy'ubwirinzi.
