Kumenya vuba no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwanduza ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu bari mu kazi.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyo muri Amerika gitanga inama ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba batanduye umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso byibuze amasaha 24 nta miti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti ihindura ibimenyetso, kandi ko politiki y'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara igomba kuba yoroshye ku buryo umukozi ashobora kuguma mu rugo kwita ku muryango urwaye, kandi ko umukozi amenya aya mategeko.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, akazi gafite ibyago byo kwandura gakubiyemo akazi gasaba ko umuntu agirana imibonano ya hafi cyangwa kenshi mu ntera ya metero esheshatu (1.8 metero) n'umuntu utazwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19, ariko ushobora kuba yaranduye SARS-CoV-2 kubera ko yakwirakwijwe mu baturage bari hafi y'aho ikorerwamo ubucuruzi, cyangwa kubera ko umuntu aherutse gukora urugendo mpuzamahanga mu gace karimo ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ubuyobozi bw'iyi kipe n'iyi kipe ifite ibyago byinshi harimo gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza guhura imbonankubone n'ibibazo by'itumanaho, gukora ingendo z'akazi zifite igihe cyo kugera/gusubirayo, guhagarika ingendo zidakenewe mu bice by'ibanze birimo icyorezo cya COVID-19, guteza imbere gahunda z'itumanaho ry'ibihe bidasanzwe harimo gusubiza impungenge z'abakozi, kongerera abakozi uburezi n'imyitozo igezweho ku bijyanye n'ibyago bya COVID-19 n'imyitwarire irinda, gutoza abakozi gukoresha imyenda n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi, gutanga ibikoresho by'isuku no gushyigikira isuku, no kuburira abakiriya ku buryo buhoraho, gushyiraho udupfukamunwa, gushyiraho udupfukamunwa cyangwa udupfukamunwa mu kazi, gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda COVID-19, gushyiraho amabarabara mu mirimo, no kuburira abakozi ku buryo bw'ibanze bakoresha.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry'abanduye, ntibakunze gukenera imashini zifasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, uburyo bwiza bwo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu bari mu ndege harimo gutandukanya abantu barwaye n'abandi bantu mu ntera y'ibirenge bitandatu, gushyiraho umukozi wo mu cyumba cyo mu ndege kugira ngo amwiteho, no guha umuntu urwaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba ko apfuka umunwa n'amaso n'umwenda mu gihe anutse cyangwa asese.
Abakozi bo mu modoka bagomba kwambara udukingirizo tw'ubuvuzi tw'akanya gato mu gihe bita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa iyo bakoreye ku bikoresho by'umubiri cyangwa ahantu hashobora kwandura, kandi wenda n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi mu gihe umurwayi arwaye afite umuriro, ananiwe guhumeka cyangwa afite ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Amasahani n'ibindi bikoresho bikoreshwa rimwe bigomba kujugunywa mu mifuka y'ibyago, kandi imiterere yangijwe igomba guhumanurwa no gukorerwa umuti nyuma. Ku ngendo z'ubucuruzi, harimo amato n'andi mato y'abagenzi, kugenzura ibyago birimo gutinda urugendo mu gihe urwaye, kwisanzura, no kumenyesha ikigo nderabuzima cyo mu bwato ako kanya niba umuntu afite umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, gukurikirana kwa muganga bikorwa mu mazu y'abantu biherereye. Uretse gukwirakwira mu baturage, ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC isaba ko hashyirwaho igihe gito cyo gusukura cyangwa se gukaraba niba umuntu ufite ubwandu yigeze kuba mu kigo cy'ishuri.
Iyo ubwandu mu baturage buri ku kigero gito cyangwa cy'ingutu, ingamba zo kugabanya imikorere y'abantu zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa, zirimo: guhagarika ingendo zo mu mirima, amateraniro n'andi makoraniro manini, urugero nk'imyitozo ngororamubiri, amasomo yo kuririmba, cyangwa gusangira mu kabari, kongera intera hagati y'ameza, ibihe byo kugera no gutaha by'agateganyo, kugabanya abasura abatabikwiriye, no gukoresha ahantu hitaruye ho kuvurira abana bafite ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane.
Iyo hari ubwandu bwinshi mu baturage, uretse ingamba zo kugabanya ubwandu, kongera igihe cyo gufunga amashuri bishobora gutekerezwa.
