OMS isaba gusa ko abantu bakoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe cyo kubaga ku kirindiro.
Ku bantu bafata ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, bita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa babatwara nta buryo bwo gukora aerosol, OMS isaba ko bakoresha udupfukamunwa, udushumi tw'ubwirinzi, cyangwa indobo z'ubuso, imyenda n'amaboko.
Iyo hatangiye gukorwa uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa kabaga gasimbuzwa imashini z'ubuhumekero za N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ku isi hose APD idahagije, OMS yasabye ko hakorwa ibishoboka byose kugira ngo APD ikoreshwe mu buryo bwa kure, hagashyirwaho inzitizi z'umubiri nka za "translucent windows", abantu bonyine bakora mu buvuzi bwa hafi bakinjira mu cyumba kirimo abarwayi ba COVID-19, hakoreshwa APD ikenewe gusa mu kazi runaka, gukomeza gukoresha uburyo bwo guhumeka bw'ubwoko bumwe mu gihe bitabwaho abarwayi benshi bafite icyorezo kimwe, kugenzura no guhuza umuyoboro w'itangwa rya APD, no kudashishikariza abantu batagira ibimenyetso gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
