b'Angiotensin modifier enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifata ku gice cyo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo (membrane y'ingirabuzimafatizo) mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ifite ibikorwa bibangamira angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE), mu kugabanya umubare wa angiotensin-II no kuzamura Angiotensin (1-7), bigatuma iba intego y'imiti yizeza yo kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'aho yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za coronavirusi zimwe.
ACE2 y'umuntu ikunze kwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin 2 ni ingirwamushinga irimo zinc iri ku butaka bw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'imbere n'iz'inyuma.
Poroteyine ACE2 ifite domain ya M2 ya peptideze ya terminal-N na domain ya transporter ya amino acid ya renal ya terminal-C ya colectrin.
ACE2 ni poroteyine imwe yo mu bwoko bwa I, ifite urubuga rw'ibinyabuzima byigenga byigaragaza ku bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu bindi binyabuzima.
Urubuga rw'ingirabuzimafatizo ya ACE2 rwashyizwe ku ruhande rw'urubuga rw'impuzu n'ikindi gikoresho cyitwa sheddase, maze poroteyine ivamo ikurwa mu maraso, igashyirwa mu cyondo.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifata ku ngirabuzimafatizo cyane cyane mu bice by'ubuhumekero by'ubwoko bwa II, mu bice by'amaraso, mu bice by'amaraso, mu bice by'amaraso, no mu bice by'amaraso.
Ibimenyetso bya mRNA ACE2 nabyo bigaragara mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, no mu gice cy'ubwonko.
Umurimo w'ibanze wa ACE2 ni ukugabanya ibyago byo kwandura.
ACE isenya ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin I mu angiotensin II ikora mu buryo bw'imikorere.
Amaherezo, ACE2 ikura amino acide phenylalanine ya karuboksi ya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayihinduranya ikavamo angiotensin (1-7) yo kwagura imitsi (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi gusenya indi peptide nyinshi zirimo [des-Arg9] -bradikinine, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura uruhu rw'ibinyabiziga bya SLC6A19 by'indobanure bya aside ya amino kandi igira uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'umwirondoro w'uruhu, ACE2 ikora nk'aho ariho ha mbere hatangirwa virusi nyinshi z'ubwoko bwa corona, zirimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ku byuma bya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 n'urusobe rwa enzymatic rwa ACE2 ku butaka bw'ingirabuzimafatizo bituma virusi n'imihindagurikire y'imihindagurikire y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu gice cy'imbere cy'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi virusi kandi isaba ko poroteyine ya S itangira gukoreshwa na serine ya protease yo mu bwoko bwa TMPRSS2, ubu ikorwaho ubushakashatsi mu buryo bwo kuvura.
Icyakora, imiryango myinshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura ibiyobyabwenge zasabye ko hakomeza gukoreshwa imiti isanzwe yo mu rwego rwa ACE na ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo bufatiweho no ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe, bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha umuti wa ACE byatumaga habaho kugabanuka kw'ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibihaha ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'abawugenzura".
Ikindi kandi, "ikoreshwa ry'umuti wa ACE ryatumye habaho kandi kugabanya ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'ibihaha mu barwayi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara z'ibihaha, cyane cyane abarwayi ba stroke n'abafite umutima udakora neza.
Gukoresha inibya ACE byongeye guhuzwa n'igabanuka ry'imfu ziterwa na pneumonia, n'ubwo ingaruka zabyo zidakomeye cyane ugereranyije n'ingaruka z'impu z'ubwonko".
ACE2 y'umuntu yongeye gutunganywa (rhACE2) iteganya kuba umuti mushya wo gukomeretsa ibihaha bikomeye, kandi igaragara ko yongerera haemodynamics y'ibihaha n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu ngurube zifite syndrome y'ubuhumekero bukomeye buterwa na lipoplisakaride.
Igihe cy'igice cya kabiri cy'umwimerere cya rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha 10 n'igihe cy'akazi k'iminota 30 uretse ko igihe cy'ingaruka ari amasaha 24.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi byerekana ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe mu barwayi batagaragaza ubukana bw'umuvuduko w'umuvuduko w'umushongi wa RAS (Renin-angiotensin system inhibitor) cyangwa mu barwayi bafite ingufu z'umuvuduko wa angiotensin II mu maraso.
b' Porogaramu ya COVID-19 ni porogaramu ya porogaramu igendanwa igamije gufasha gukurikirana guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020, ni ukuvuga igikorwa cyo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye.
Hariho porogaramu nyinshi zagiye zitegurwa cyangwa zashyizweho, zashyigikiwe na leta mu bihugu byinshi.
Hari ingamba zo kubaka porogaramu yo gukurikirana abo bahuye nazo.
Ikibazo cy'ibanga cyashidikanyijweho, cyane cyane ku bijyanye na sisitemu ishingiye ku guhitamo aho umuntu akorera.
Ubundi buryo budahabanye cyane n'ibanga ry'umuntu, ni ugukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu amenye aho ari hafi y'undi muntu.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byombi byatangaje ko bizashyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu y'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyize hanze porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba barahuye n'abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Iyi porogaramu ikoreshwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango wa IT wo mu karere, yashyizwe hanze nk'isoko ryugurutse kandi izashyikirizwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije "StopKorona!", porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth igamije gukurikirana abantu bashobora kwandura no gutanga ibisubizo byihuse ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itangazamakuru n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza tariki ya 14 Mata 2020, iyo porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu iri mu cyiciro cy'iterambere kandi ko izaboneka mu byumweru bike.
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande zirimo gusuzuma porogaramu ishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether ya Singapore na protocole ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite umugambi wo gutangiza porogaramu ya geofencing ku barwayi ba COVID-19 basanganywe mu mujyi wa Moscou; iyi porogaramu igamije kwemeza ko batagomba kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ko hari ibibazo by'ingirakamaro bishobora kuvuka mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, hakubiyemo ibinyoma by'uko ari byo by'ukuri, n'uko bishobora kutagira icyo bigeraho mu gihe porogaramu ya porogaramu yaba ikoresha abantu bake cyane.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'imirimo ya "coronavirus" ibeshya cyangwa iteje akaga, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo imikoreshereze ijyanye na coronavirus kuri App Store, aribyo guhagarika gusa imiryango "yemewe" cyangwa ifite izina ryiza.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikiye ubwiru bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi bakoresheje porogaramu za coronavirus, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa remezo by'iperereza byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizakurwaho nyuma y'uko iterabwoba rirangiye.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko habaho imipaka ku buryo bwo kugenzura.
Iri shyirahamwe ryatanze ibisabwa umunani ku mushinga wa leta:
kugenzura bigomba kuba "bikwiriye, bikenewe kandi bihuje n'amategeko";
kongereraho kugenzura no kurinda bigomba kuba bifite icyemezo cy'izuba rirenze;
ikoreshwa ry'amakuru rigomba guhagarikwa mu rwego rwa COVID-19;
umutekano n'ubujiji by'ibyangombwa bigomba kurindwa kandi bigaragarira mu bimenyetso;
kugenzura mu buryo bwa digitale bigomba kwirinda ivangura no kwirengagiza;
gusangira amakuru n'abandi bantu bigomba gusobanurwa mu mategeko;
hagomba kubaho uburinzi ku ihohoterwa n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage bwo kwitaba ihohoterwa;
Kwifatanya bivuze ko "abafite uruhare bose" bakeneye, harimo abahanga mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda y'abasizwe.
Gahunda ya Google/Apple iteganijwe ni ugukemura ikibazo cy'uburinzi buhoraho binyuze mu gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga ibikoresho bitagikenewe.
Ibihugu bimwe bikoresha imbuga zishingiye ku rubuga, aho gukoresha porogaramu, bityo bigatuma udakenera gukuramo porogaramu no kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, hashyizweho uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite uburyo bwo kubona amakuru y'aho umuntu ari byashoboraga guteza ibibazo bikomeye by'ibanga.
Icyakora, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri z'icyicaro gikuru zikeneye kubona amakuru yerekeye ahantu umuntu aba; hari sisitemu zimwe na zimwe z'ibanga zashyizweho zikoresha seriveri z'icicaro gikuru gusa mu itumanaho (reba igice kiri hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hari uburyo butari bwo bwo gukurikirana abantu bakorana na telefoni.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu ikusanya amakuru yo gukurikirana ku bikoresho bitandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'amakuru y'ubucuruzi bw'ikarita, kandi ikomatanya aya makuru kugira ngo itange imenyesha ry'ubutumwa bw'ibanga ku bantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Uretse gukoresha aya makuru mu kuburira abantu bashobora guhura na yo, leta yashyize aya makuru ku mugaragaro, ibyo bikaba byaratumye habaho impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko agenga ubuzima bwite bw'abantu nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS.
Ibi ni amakuru aboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze kuri porogaramu nyinshi na site za interineti. Ibihugu nka Ubudage birimo gutekereza gukoresha sisitemu ziganjemo kimwe kimwe n'ibikingira ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru arambuye ntabwo aratangazwa.
Gukurikirana abantu bakwirakwiza amakuru ku buryo bw'ibanga ni igitekerezo cyamaze gushyirwa mu bikorwa, hamwe n'ibitabo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi byatangiye guhera nibura mu mwaka wa 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi y'impuguke yakoraga ku bisubizo by'ubwirinzi, nko gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE), kugira ngo bandike aho umuntu ari hafi y'undi muntu.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni gahunda yo guhuza irimo uburyo bwihariye kandi bwigenga, ntabwo ari protocol imwe.
Muri ubu buryo, amakuru yihariye ashobora kumenyekana ntajya asiba igikoresho, kandi guhuza byose bibera mu gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga muri MIT Media Lab ryatangije SafePaths, urubuga rwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga ririnda ubuzima bwite mu gihe cyo gukusanya no gukoresha amakuru yerekeye aho cyangwa intera y'umurongo kugira ngo bakurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Ibi bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gitabo cyitwa "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho by'ibanga rikomeye kugira ngo rifashe abakoresha gusangira amakuru ahereranye n'aho bari n'ubuzima bwabo n'abandi bakoresha n'abashinzwe umutekano, nta guhara ubwiru bw'ayo makuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, ishyirahamwe ry'isi yose rya TCN ryashinzwe n'amatsinda afite uburyo bumwe kandi ari poroteyine nyinshi zisubiranamo, agamije kugabanya gutandukana no kwemerera imikoranire ku isi yose y'ibikoresho byo gukurikirana no kuburira, ari nacyo kintu cy'ingenzi mu kugera ku kwemerwa mu buryo bwagutse.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, leta ya Singapore yatangaje ko yashyize mu isoko rya BlueTrace protocol ikoreshwa na porogaramu yemewe na leta yayo.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, sosiyete itegeka urubuga rwa mobile rwa Android na iOS, batangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abo bahuye, bavuga ko izarinda ubuzima bwite, ishingiye ku ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy na cryptography irinda ubuzima bwite.
Nanone batangaje ibihereranye n'ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanze rikoreshwa muri ubwo buryo.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, iyi gahunda igomba gutangwa mu byiciro bitatu:
gushyira ku isoko ibikoresho byatuma leta ikora porogaramu yemewe yo gukurikirana coronavirus ikingira ubuzima bwite
Google na Apple bateganya gukemura ikibazo cyo gufata amakuru no kugenzura byimbitse babanje gutanga sisitemu binyuze mu kuvugurura sisitemu y'imikorere, hanyuma bakazivanaho muburyo bumwe nyuma yuko ibyago birangiye.
b'Igikorwa cyo guhindura umuti (cyitwa kandi gushyiraho indi ntego nshya, uburyo bushya, cyangwa inshingano nshya ku muti cyangwa guhindura uburyo bwo kuwufata) ni ugukoresha umuti wemewe ku muti mushya, ari wo wavuye mu ndwara cyangwa mu burwayi butandukanye n'intumbero y'amajyambere y'umuti.
Uru rugendo ni rwo rugendo rw'ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bukomeje gukorwa mu rwego rwo gukora imiti ya COVID-19 ifite umutekano kandi ikora.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwerekeranye no gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 no guterwa plasma mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zishobora kuba intumbero y'imiti, buri poroteyine ikaba ifite imbuga nyinshi zo guhuza ligase.
Isesengura ry'ibibanza byo gufatiraho ibyo byuma bishobora kuba urufatiro rw'umushinga wo gukora imiti ya virusi ikora ku poroteyine ya COVID-19.
Zimwe mu poroteyine z'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 yibasira ni protease imeze nka papain, RNA-dependent polymerase, helicases, protein S, na ADP ribophosphatease.
Hussein A A, et al basuzumye ibirungo byinshi by'abakandida hanyuma babishyira mu bikorwa, basuzuma ko bifite imiterere isa n'iy'imiti yemewe kandi ifite imiterere isa n'iy'imiti ikomeye cyane, kugira ngo bongere iterambere ry'imiti ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukoreshwa mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'igerageza ry'ubushakashatsi kugira ngo ishyirwe mu bikorwa mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'igerageza.
Chlorokuine ni umuti urwanya malariya ukoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara zimwe na zimwe ziterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chlorokuin na hydrochlorokuin bifitanye isano ari bibiri mu miti ine izakorwaho ubushakashatsi mu rwego rw'igerageza ry'ubuvuzi rya Solidarity.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cuomo, yatangaje ko igerageza rya chloroquine na hydrochlorquine muri New York rizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquine phosphate hashingiwe ku Burenganzira bw'Ikibazo cy'Igikoresho (EUA).
Iyi miti ntirahabwa uruhushya na FDA mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi kandi yemejwe hakurikijwe EUA gusa nk'ubuvuzi bw'igerageza bwo gukoreshwa mu buryo bw'ibanze mu barwayi bari mu bitaro, ariko ntibashobora kubona imiti mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
CDC ivuga ko "imikoreshereze, ingano cyangwa igihe cy'ibanze cya hydroxychloroquine mu kwirinda cyangwa kuvura SARS-CoV-2" bitarafatwa.
Abaganga bavuga ko bakoreshaga imiti iyo "hari nta yandi mahitamo".
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Turukiya bari i Istanbul barimo bakora ubushakashatsi buto ku birebana no gukoresha chlorokuin, ikajyanirana na zinc, vitamine A, vitamine C na vitamine D.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye burimo gukorwa kuri kaminuza ya Duke na kaminuza ya Oxford.
Ishuri ry'Ubuvuzi rya NYU Langone ririmo gukora igerageza ryo gusuzuma niba umuti wa hydroxychloroquine ufite ubushobozi bwo gukumira indwara.
Ibizamini by'ubuvuzi by'Abashinwa i Wuhan na Shenzhen bivuga ko favipiravir yagaragaye ko "igaragara ko ifite imbaraga".
Abarwayi 35 bo muri Shenzhen bagaragaje ko batanduye mu minsi 4, mu gihe abarwayi 45 batigeze bahabwa imiti bari barwaye iminsi 11.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan ku barwayi 240 barwaye pneumonia, kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bahawe favipiravir ikindi kimwe cya kabiri cyahawe umifenovir.
