Ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya lopinavir/ritonavir (Kaletra), ari cyo cyorezo cya lopinavir n'igitera ritonavir, bwasobanuye ko nta nyungu zagaragaye.
Iyi miti igamije guhagarika ubwandu bwa virusi itera SIDA mu buryo bwo gufunga protease.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri kaminuza ya Colorado barimo kugerageza guhindura imiti kugira ngo babone imiti izashyirwamo protease ya SARS-CoV-2.
