Remdesivir yakozwe kandi ivugwa cyane na Gilead Sciences nk'umuti wa Ebola virus disease na Marburg virus infection. Nyuma, Gilead Sciences yaje kubona ko Remdesivir ifite ibikorwa bya antiviral in vitro kuri filiyo-, pneumo-, paramikso-, na coronavirus.
