Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere kuri SARS-CoV bwakoreshejwe kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 receptors mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu.
Hari uburyo butatu bw'inkingo bukomeje gushakishwa.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi bifuza gukora urukingo rwa virusi yose.
Gukoresha virusi, yaba idafite ubuzima cyangwa ipfuye, bigamije guhita itangiza ubwirinzi bw'umubiri w'umuntu ku ndwara nshya ya COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, urukingo rwa subunit, bugamije gukora urukingo rutuma abasoda b'umubiri bagira ibyiyumvo ku byiciro runaka bya virusi.
Mu gihe cya SARS-CoV-2, ubushakashatsi bwibanze ku poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi kwinjira mu gikoresho cya ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni urukingo rwa aside ya nucleotide (urukingo rwa ADN cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo z'ubushakashatsi zikorerwa kuri ubwo buryo zigomba kugeragezwa kugira ngo zimenye niba ari nziza cyangwa ari mbi. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, hatangiye igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ku bantu bane bitangiye gukora mu bitaro bya Seattle.
Urukingo rufite kode ya gakondo idateza indwara ikururwa na virusi itera indwara.
Hari ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi birenga 300 birimo gukorwa muri Mata 2020.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumye imiti yemewe ya malariya, harimo n'icya kane cy'imiyoborere y'ibinyabutabire bya hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chlorquine.
Imiti ya antiviral ihabwa intego nshya ni yo igize igice kinini cy'ubushakashatsi bw'Abashinwa, aho mu bihugu byinshi habaye ibizamini icyenda by'icyiciro cya gatatu bya remdesivir, bikaba byari biteganyijwe ko izajya itanga raporo mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa kane.
Muri Mata 2020, ubushakashatsi bwihuse ku iterambere ry'imiti n'inkingo bya COVID-19 byari byamaze gutangwa. Imiti myinshi ya antiviral irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir, na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Muri Werurwe 2020, hari ibimenyetso by'agateganyo byerekana ko remdesivir ari umuti w'ingenzi.
Ihinduka ry'imiterere ry'uburwayi ryagaragaye mu barwayi bavurwa na remdesivir mu gihe cy'ubutabazi.
Icyiciro cya III cy'igerageza ry'ubuvuzi kirimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.
Icyakora, hari abantu basabye ko icyo gitabo cyakorwa n'abandi bantu.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya no mu Bushinwa batanze inama yo gukoresha chlorokuin.
Ariko kandi, Ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe Virology, n'ubwo cyatangaje ingano ya gramu imwe ku munsi, cyatangaje ko incuro ebyiri ari mbi cyane kandi ko bishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uburenganzira bwo gukoresha mu buryo bw'ibanze za hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ku bw'amabwiriza y'abaganga bavura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko ingano yo hejuru ya ribavirin ikenewe mu guhagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bwa in vitro.
Nitazoksanide yashyizwe ahagaragara mu bindi byigwa bya in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ihagaritse mu rugero ruciriritse. Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko gutangira gutangiza poroteyine ya protene ya protene ya transmembrane 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi cyane mu kwinjira kwa SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhuza na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi ku chlorokuin na hydroxychloroquine hamwe cyangwa nta azitromycin bifite aho bigarukira cyane cyane ko byabujije umuryango w'ubuvuzi gukoresha ubu buvuzi nta kindi cyifuzo cy'ubushakashatsi. Oseltamivir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bwa in vitro kandi nta ruhare ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibibazo by'umuyaga wa cytokine bishobora kubaho mu gihe COVID-19 iri mu cyiciro cya nyuma.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira imiterere ya antistokin. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'Ubushinwa nyuma y'uko ubushakashatsi buto bwarangiye.
Iyi miti iri mu igerageza ry'icyiciro cya kabiri ry'icyiciro cya kabiri mu gihugu cyose mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ibisubizo byiza ku bantu barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Iyo ivanzwe n'ibipimo by'amaraso bya feritine ya serum kugira ngo hamenyekane cytocin storm, iyi miti igamije kurwanya cytocin storm, byibwira ko ari yo ihitana bamwe mu bantu bayifiteho.
Mu mwaka wa 2017, interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bw'urubanza rwasubukuwe ku buvuzi bw'indwara yo kurekura sitokine ya steroid idahinduka iturutse ku mpamvu zitandukanye, ari zo CAR T cell therapy.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso by'amahirwe cyangwa by'ibanze byerekana ko tocilizumab ari umuti w'ingirakamaro wa CRS.
